#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter6/39_Oofs_Fortress.cfg:28
msgid "Io"
msgstr "Io"

#. [side]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:322
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:400
msgid "Caged"
msgstr "Enjaulado"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:366
msgid "Finally. The bridge to Zei should be not far south."
msgstr "Finalmente. El puente a Zei no debería estar lejos al sur."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:370
msgid "Let's hurry to Zei before something happens."
msgstr "Apresurémonos a Zei antes de que algo pase."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:374
msgid ""
"If possible, it would be nice to kill any orcs we encounter. Our friends "
"have suffered enough already."
msgstr ""
"Si es posible, sería bueno matar a cualquier orco que encontremos. Nuestros "
"amigos han sufrido suficiente ya."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:388
msgid "Excuse me, do you happen to know what happened to the bridge?"
msgstr "Disculpe, ¿sabe qué pasó con el puente?"

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:392
msgid "Damn orcs happened."
msgstr "Los malditos orcos pasaron."

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:396
msgid "I know one is as bad as another but that’s the last straw."
msgstr ""
"Sé que uno es tan malo como otro pero eso es la gota que colma el vaso."

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:400
msgid ""
"They burnt the damn bridge down, then tried to cross it with their wagons "
"while it was still on fire!"
msgstr ""
"¡Quemaron el maldito puente, luego intentaron cruzarlo con sus carretas "
"mientras aún estaba en llamas!"

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:404
msgid ""
"They lost half-a-dozen orcs and sabotaged their own flight plan by "
"destroying the bridge."
msgstr ""
"Perdieron media docena de orcos y sabotearon su propio plan de huida al "
"destruir el puente."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:408
msgid "Do you know if there is another way to reach Zei?"
msgstr "¿Sabe si hay otra forma de llegar a Zei?"

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:412
msgid ""
"Now, the only way to reach Zei is to pass through the old crypts by taking "
"that road there. "
msgstr ""
"Ahora, la única forma de llegar a Zei es pasar por las antiguas criptas "
"tomando ese camino allí. "

#. [message], speaker=Ek
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:416
msgid ""
"But don’t count on me coming with you. The way is probably full of orcs."
msgstr ""
"Pero no cuentes conmigo para ir contigo. El camino probablemente está lleno "
"de orcos."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:440
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:547
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:613
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:661
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:709
msgid "There is a bat in this cage. Should I open it?"
msgstr "Hay un murciélago en esta jaula. ¿Debo abrirla?"

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:442
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:549
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:615
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:663
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:711
msgid "Yes, free it."
msgstr "Sí, libéralo."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:460
msgid "It is free, but I don't think it was a safe idea."
msgstr "Está libre, pero no creo que fuera una idea segura."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:465
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:572
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:638
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:686
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:734
msgid "No, it's not a good idea. It could attack you."
msgstr "No, no es una buena idea. Podría atacarte."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:488
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:620
msgid "The staff of the statue looks like a lever. Should I try pulling it?"
msgstr "El bastón de la estatua parece una palanca. ¿Debo intentar jalarla?"

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:490
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:510
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:553
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:632
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:769
msgid "Yes, do it."
msgstr "Sí, hazlo."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:536
msgid "It looks like it opened the entrance of a secret tunnel."
msgstr "Parece que abrió la entrada de un túnel secreto."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:541
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:638
msgid "No, it might be a trap."
msgstr "No, podría ser una trampa."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:559
msgid ""
"North : Arable Highlands\n"
"West : Crypt of the Sacred Blood\n"
"South : Zei"
msgstr ""
"Norte : Tierras Altas Arables\n"
"Oeste : Cripta de la Sangre Sagrada\n"
"Sur : Zei"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:579
msgid "South : Crypt of the Sacred Blood"
msgstr "Sur : Cripta de la Sangre Sagrada"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:597
msgid "West : Crypt of the Sacred Blood"
msgstr "Oeste : Cripta de la Sangre Sagrada"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:655
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:686
msgid "I found the entrance of the crypt."
msgstr "Encontré la entrada de la cripta."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:659
msgid ""
"I'm a bit worried of what we might find inside, but we have no other choice "
"if we want to reach Zei. Let's enter the crypt but be careful everyone."
msgstr ""
"Estoy un poco preocupado por lo que podríamos encontrar adentro, pero no "
"tenemos otra opción si queremos llegar a Zei. Entremos a la cripta pero sean "
"cuidadosos todos."

#. [message]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:681
msgid ""
"I don't see any more orc around here. We can continue our journey knowing "
"that our friends will have a least a break."
msgstr ""
"No veo más orcos por aquí. Podemos continuar nuestro viaje sabiendo que "
"nuestros amigos tendrán al menos un respiro."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:717
msgid "Suddenly..."
msgstr "De repente..."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:724
msgid "What is that?! A walking skeleton! What is happening here?!"
msgstr "¡¿Qué es eso?! ¡Un esqueleto andante! ¡¿Qué está pasando aquí?!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:755
msgid "Alas..."
msgstr "Ay..."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:759
msgid ""
"The bridge! It is destroyed! What happened there?! How will we be able to "
"rally Zei now?"
msgstr ""
"¡El puente! ¡Está destruido! ¡¿Qué pasó allí?! ¡¿Cómo podremos llegar a Zei "
"ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/03_Bridge_to_Zei.cfg:772
msgid ""
"It will be too dangerous entering the crypt if someone is animating the "
"dead. We'd better find a way to repair the bridge"
msgstr ""
"Será demasiado peligroso entrar a la cripta si alguien está animando a los "
"muertos. Mejor encontramos una forma de reparar el puente"

#. [scenario], id=04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:4
msgid "Crypt of the Sacred Blood"
msgstr "Cripta de la Sangre Sagrada"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:35
msgid "Reach the exit of the crypt"
msgstr "Alcanza la salida de la cripta"

#. [side], type=Deathblade
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:85
msgid "Skeletons"
msgstr "Esqueletos"

#. [side], type=Gargoyle
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:154
msgid "Gargoyles"
msgstr "Gárgolas"

#. [unit], id=Lujeje, type=Initiate, gender=female
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:428
msgid "Lujeje"
msgstr "Lujeje"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:479
msgid "This skeleton we've seen up there is worrying."
msgstr "Este esqueleto que vimos arriba es preocupante."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:483
msgid ""
"I hope no one has had the idea to animate the dead that can be found in this "
"crypt."
msgstr ""
"Espero que nadie haya tenido la idea de animar a los muertos que se pueden "
"encontrar en esta cripta."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:487
msgid "Anyway, we have no choice. We must cross this crypt to reach Zei. "
msgstr ""
"De todos modos, no tenemos opción. Debemos cruzar esta cripta para llegar a "
"Zei. "

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:508
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:630
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:811
msgid "There is a large wooden door. Should I try to open it?"
msgstr "Hay una gran puerta de madera. ¿Debo intentar abrirla?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:528
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:651
msgid "Part of the wall fell when I opened the door."
msgstr "Parte de la pared cayó cuando abrí la puerta."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:533
msgid "Wait a bit. We'll have to open it but don't do it right now."
msgstr "Espera un poco. Tendremos que abrirla pero no lo hagas ahora."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:551
msgid "There is a lever on the floor. Should I pull it?"
msgstr "Hay una palanca en el piso. ¿Debo jalarla?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:581
msgid "It has opened a portion of the wall."
msgstr "Ha abierto una porción de la pared."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:602
msgid "The portion of wall is closed back."
msgstr "La porción de pared se cerró de nuevo."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:609
msgid "No, not now."
msgstr "No, no ahora."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:656
msgid "No, I don't want to know what's behind."
msgstr "No, no quiero saber qué hay detrás."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:687
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:949
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:993
msgid "Argh! I'm burning! There was a trap."
msgstr "¡Argh! ¡Me quemo! Había una trampa."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:731
msgid "Argh! I'm burning! The floor is trapped."
msgstr "¡Argh! ¡Me quemo! El piso está atrapado."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:767
msgid "There are two large wooden doors. Should I try to open them?"
msgstr "Hay dos grandes puertas de madera. ¿Debo intentar abrirlas?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:783
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:827
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:913
msgid "It's opened."
msgstr "Está abierta."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:788
msgid "Wait a bit. We'll have to open them but don't do it right now."
msgstr "Espera un poco. Tendremos que abrirlas pero no lo hagas ahora."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:813
msgid "Yes, let's quit this room."
msgstr "Sí, salgamos de esta habitación."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:832
msgid "No. I'm afraid of what will happen if we open it."
msgstr "No. Tengo miedo de lo que pasará si la abrimos."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:877
msgid "Well, that's not good."
msgstr "Bueno, eso no es bueno."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:897
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1210
msgid ""
"This block of stone looks like a large stone door. Should I try to open it?"
msgstr ""
"Este bloque de piedra parece una gran puerta de piedra. ¿Debo intentar "
"abrirla?"

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:899
msgid "Yes, let's see what's behind."
msgstr "Sí, veamos qué hay detrás."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1056
msgid ""
"You’re either a hero or the most stupid person I ever met. Either way, thank "
"you."
msgstr ""
"Eres un héroe o la persona más estúpida que he conocido. De cualquier modo, "
"gracias."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1062
msgid "I’m Lujeje, the initiate."
msgstr "Soy Lujeje, la iniciada."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1066
msgid "What are initiates?"
msgstr "¿Qué son los iniciados?"

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1070
msgid "We are people who devote their life to knowledge."
msgstr "Somos personas que dedican su vida al conocimiento."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1074
msgid ""
"Through knowledge, one can acquire powers over natural forces, allowing "
"initiates to master magic. Some of us become healers, others turn to more "
"destructive applications of knowledge."
msgstr ""
"A través del conocimiento, uno puede adquirir poderes sobre las fuerzas "
"naturales, permitiendo a los iniciados dominar la magia. Algunos de nosotros "
"nos convertimos en sanadores, otros recurren a aplicaciones más destructivas "
"del conocimiento."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1078
msgid "It would be useful to have a healer with us."
msgstr "Sería útil tener un sanador con nosotros."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1089
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:399
msgid "Are you alright?"
msgstr "¿Estás bien?"

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1093
msgid ""
"One more day spent translating the gravestone inscriptions for the orcs and "
"I would have become as mad as them. But now I should be fine."
msgstr ""
"Un día más traduciendo las inscripciones de las lápidas para los orcos y me "
"habría vuelto tan loco como ellos. Pero ahora debería estar bien."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1104
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2016
msgid "What are you doing here?"
msgstr "¿Qué haces aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1108
msgid ""
"Orcs kidnapped me while I was studying the crypt. I'm writing my thesis on "
"the Crypt of the Sacred Blood. But I'm only beginning."
msgstr ""
"Los orcos me secuestraron mientras estudiaba la cripta. Estoy escribiendo mi "
"tesis sobre la Cripta de la Sangre Sagrada. Pero apenas estoy comenzando."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1112
msgid ""
"The orcs wanted me to translate what is written on those tombs. In the "
"meantime, they started to raise skeletons."
msgstr ""
"Los orcos querían que tradujera lo que está escrito en esas tumbas. Mientras "
"tanto, comenzaron a levantar esqueletos."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1116
msgid ""
"Those brainless thugs barely understand fire. How could they master "
"necromancy? This does not bode well, but I doubt we will learn more here."
msgstr ""
"Esos matones sin cerebro apenas entienden el fuego. ¿Cómo podrían dominar la "
"nigromancia? Esto no augura nada bueno, pero dudo que aprendamos más aquí."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1127
msgid "Do you know how to get out of here?"
msgstr "¿Sabes cómo salir de aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1131
msgid "There is an exit north."
msgstr "Hay una salida al norte."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1142
msgid "Can we help you?"
msgstr "¿Podemos ayudarte?"

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1147
msgid "Actually, yes. Would you mind me coming with you?"
msgstr "De hecho, sí. ¿Te importaría que vaya contigo?"

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1149
msgid "No, come with us."
msgstr "No, ven con nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1164
msgid ""
"Thank you. I didn’t like the idea of having to stay here by myself anymore."
msgstr "Gracias. No me gustaba la idea de tener que quedarme aquí solo ya."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1168
msgid ""
"Lujeje is a hero. Heroes, of whom you will soon have a  collection, will "
"always be recalled automatically. Heroes can pick up and equip items. Once "
"recruited, they will provide you with an additional unit type to recruit. If "
"a hero dies, you will not be able to recruit this unit type anymore."
msgstr ""
"Lujeje es un héroe. Los héroes, de los que pronto tendrás una colección, "
"serán siempre reincorporados automáticamente. Los héroes pueden recoger y "
"equipar objetos. Una vez reclutados, te proporcionarán un tipo de unidad "
"adicional para reclutar. Si un héroe muere, no podrás reclutar este tipo de "
"unidad ya."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1172
msgid "You can now recruit initiates."
msgstr "Ahora puedes reclutar iniciados."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1177
msgid "Yes, I'm better by myself."
msgstr "Sí, estoy mejor solo."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1181
msgid ""
"(angry) Alright. But don’t worry, I’m sure I’ll be fine, alone, with no "
"weapon and in the middle of the orcs and other monsters. Best regards!"
msgstr ""
"(enojado) Está bien. Pero no te preocupes, estoy seguro de que estaré bien, "
"solo, sin arma y en medio de los orcos y otros monstruos. ¡Saludos!"

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1195
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:652
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:894
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1776
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2121
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2209
msgid "Leave"
msgstr "Salir"

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1212
msgid "Yes, let's quit this crypt."
msgstr "Sí, salgamos de esta cripta."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1222
msgid "No, I have some more things to do before leaving the crypt."
msgstr "No, tengo algunas cosas más que hacer antes de dejar la cripta."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/04_Crypt_of_the_Sacred_Blood.cfg:1231
msgid ""
"The crypt really is a mortal maze. I don't think we will be able to get out "
"of here alive."
msgstr ""
"La cripta realmente es un laberinto mortal. No creo que podamos salir de "
"aquí vivos."

#. [scenario], id=05_Reaching_Zei
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:33
msgid "Reaching Zei"
msgstr "Llegando a Zei"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:80
msgid "Reach Zei with a hero"
msgstr "Llega a Zei con un héroe"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:85
msgid "Defeat all orcish leaders"
msgstr "Derrota a todos los líderes orcos"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:434
msgid "I'm glad we are finally out of that crypt."
msgstr "Me alegra que finalmente salgamos de esa cripta."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:438
msgid ""
"However, I'm quite worried by what we have seen down there. Who would have "
"thought that orcs could master necromancy?"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, estoy bastante preocupado por lo que vimos allí abajo. ¿Quién "
"habría pensado que los orcos podrían dominar la nigromancia?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:442
msgid ""
"Anyway, we only need to go down this mountain and we will reach Zei. I hope "
"it is not too late to bring the message."
msgstr ""
"De todos modos, solo necesitamos bajar esta montaña y llegaremos a Zei. "
"Espero que no sea demasiado tarde para llevar el mensaje."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:452
msgid ""
"I would like to help you, but I would need a better staff and an armour. Can "
"you please lend me this?"
msgstr ""
"Me gustaría ayudarte, pero necesitaría un mejor bastón y una armadura. "
"¿Puedes prestarme esto por favor?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:456
msgid "Sure, no problem. We have some items that we are not using."
msgstr "Claro, no hay problema. Tenemos algunos objetos que no estamos usando."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:460
msgid "You can equip items on your other heroes the same way you equip Io."
msgstr ""
"Puedes equipar objetos en tus otros héroes de la misma forma que equipas a "
"Io."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:464
msgid "Do you know how to get to Zei from here?"
msgstr "¿Sabes cómo llegar a Zei desde aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:468
msgid "There are two ways. We can either take the main road or the pass."
msgstr "Hay dos formas. Podemos tomar el camino principal o el paso."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:472
msgid ""
"The main road goes north to avoid the mountains then go back south-west. "
"There is also a mountain road that goes north-west directly to Zei, but it "
"might not be faster as it is very narrow."
msgstr ""
"El camino principal va al norte para evitar las montañas y luego regresa al "
"suroeste. También hay un camino de montaña que va al noroeste directamente a "
"Zei, pero podría no ser más rápido ya que es muy estrecho."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:489
msgid ""
"This is where the two roads split. The pass is north-west from here while "
"the main road continue north-east."
msgstr ""
"Aquí es donde se dividen los dos caminos. El paso está al noroeste desde "
"aquí mientras que el camino principal continúa al noreste."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:506
msgid "South: Crypt of the Sacred Blood"
msgstr "Sur: Cripta de la Sangre Sagrada"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:524
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:590
msgid "North: Zei"
msgstr "Norte: Zei"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:567
msgid "It is as free as one can be."
msgstr "Está tan libre como uno puede ser."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:633
msgid "It is now free to attack whoever it wants."
msgstr "Ahora está libre para atacar a quien quiera."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:681
msgid "Free and evil."
msgstr "Libre y malvado."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:729
msgid "It's free. But I don't know if it's good for us."
msgstr "Está libre. Pero no sé si es bueno para nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:757
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:814
msgid ""
"With only a name given by a dying friend, our shattered hero is crossing "
"Zei’s doors, marked by fights."
msgstr ""
"Con solo un nombre dado por un amigo moribundo, nuestro héroe destrozado "
"cruza las puertas de Zei, marcado por luchas."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:761
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:818
msgid ""
"Who could have then imagined that the arrival of a humble farmer was going "
"to change forever the future of the kingdom?"
msgstr ""
"¿Quién podría haber imaginado entonces que la llegada de un humilde granjero "
"iba a cambiar para siempre el futuro del reino?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:773
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:902
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/12_Mine_Rats.cfg:1422
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/13_Miners_life.cfg:1461
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/14_Mine_maze.cfg:1555
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:1517
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the orcs here!"
msgstr "¡Espérennos! ¡Aún estamos luchando contra los orcos aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:797
msgid ""
"That's it. We defeated the orcish leaders that were pillaging the region."
msgstr "Eso es. Derrotamos a los líderes orcos que saqueaban la región."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:801
msgid "I found the valuables they had accumulated."
msgstr "Encontré los objetos valiosos que habían acumulado."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:805
msgid ""
"I do not think we will be able to find their rightful owners, but let's keep "
"them. \n"
"We can now go to Zei without having to worry about what we leave behind us."
msgstr ""
"No creo que podamos encontrar a sus legítimos dueños, pero guardémoslos. \n"
"Ahora podemos ir a Zei sin tener que preocuparnos por lo que dejamos atrás."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter1/05_Reaching_Zei.cfg:834
msgid ""
"There are too many orcs between us and Zei. The city has probably fallen "
"already. Everything is lost."
msgstr ""
"Hay demasiados orcos entre nosotros y Zei. La ciudad probablemente ya cayó. "
"Todo está perdido."

#. [scenario], id=06_Zei
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:4
msgid "Zei"
msgstr "Zei"

#. [part]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:24
msgid ""
"With only a name given by a dying friend, our shattered hero is crossing "
"Zei’s doors, marked by fights. \n"
"Who could have then imagined that the arrival of a humble farmer was going "
"to change forever the future of the kingdom?"
msgstr ""
"Con solo un nombre dado por un amigo moribundo, nuestro héroe destrozado "
"cruza las puertas de Zei, marcado por luchas. \n"
"¿Quién podría haber imaginado entonces que la llegada de un humilde granjero "
"iba a cambiar para siempre el futuro del reino?"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:52
msgid "Find and talk to Csia"
msgstr "Encuentra y habla con Csia"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:69
msgid "Kill the monsters on the beach."
msgstr "Mata a los monstruos en la playa."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:81
msgid "Buy some food and find a way to carry it. You have $food_counter| food."
msgstr ""
"Compra algo de comida y encuentra una forma de llevarla. Tienes "
"$food_counter| comida."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:93
msgid "Buy at least 5 food. You have $food_counter| food."
msgstr "Compra al menos 5 comida. Tienes $food_counter| comida."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:98
msgid "Leave Zei to Udxatfe"
msgstr "Sal de Zei a Udxatfe"

#. [message], speaker=Gumthynaent
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:299
msgid "Welcome to Zei, stranger."
msgstr "Bienvenido a Zei, extraño."

#. [message], speaker=Gumthynaent
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:303
msgid ""
"You managed to clear yourself a path through this orcish jungle? I imagine "
"the hordes of savages that went through here last night continued to the "
"Arable Highlands."
msgstr ""
"¿Lograste abrirte un camino a través de esta jungla orca? Imagino que las "
"hordas de salvajes que pasaron por aquí anoche continuaron a las Tierras "
"Altas Arables."

#. [message], speaker=Gumthynaent
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:311
msgid ""
"I'm sorry for the loss of your friends. Please excuse us for this mess. We "
"have been unable to mend the hurts caused by the orcish waves."
msgstr ""
"Lamento la pérdida de tus amigos. Por favor excúsanos por este desastre. No "
"hemos podido reparar los daños causados por las olas orcas."

#. [message], speaker=Gumthynaent
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:315
msgid ""
"I think most shops are open, but, because of the orc's looting, there must "
"not be much available."
msgstr ""
"Creo que la mayoría de las tiendas están abiertas, pero, por el saqueo de "
"los orcos, no debe haber mucho disponible."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:319
msgid ""
"We will probably go look anyway. We have items to sell and gold to buy with."
msgstr ""
"Probablemente iremos a mirar de todos modos. Tenemos objetos para vender y "
"oro para comprar."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:333
msgid "Excuse me. Do you happen to be Csia?"
msgstr "Disculpe. ¿Es usted Csia?"

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Guardian
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:337
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:816
msgid "Yes I am."
msgstr "Sí, lo soy."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:341
msgid ""
"If you’re here to seek help, don’t count on it. What the orcs couldn’t take "
"was destroyed or burnt."
msgstr ""
"Si estás aquí para buscar ayuda, no cuentes con ella. Lo que los orcos no "
"pudieron llevar fue destruido o quemado."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:345
msgid ""
"They even burnt Reaper, my good old catapult… although it hadn’t thrown a "
"stone for so many years."
msgstr ""
"Incluso quemaron a Reaper, mi buena vieja catapulta… aunque no había lanzado "
"una piedra por tantos años."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:378
msgid "What can I do for you?"
msgstr "¿Qué puedo hacer por ti?"

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:380
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1651
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2001
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr "¿Quién eres?"

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:384
msgid ""
"Excuse me, who are you exactly? I was only given your name by a dying friend "
"to come for help and I don't know much more."
msgstr ""
"Disculpe, ¿quién es usted exactamente? Solo me dieron su nombre por un amigo "
"moribundo para venir por ayuda y no sé mucho más."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Guardian
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:388
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:849
msgid "I'm Csia, mayor of Zei."
msgstr "Soy Csia, alcalde de Zei."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:403
msgid "Don't worry about me. I have seen worse during the war."
msgstr "No te preocupes por mí. He visto peor durante la guerra."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:414
msgid "Do you have more information about what happened here?"
msgstr "¿Tienes más información sobre lo que pasó aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:418
msgid "Not much."
msgstr "No mucho."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:422
msgid ""
"But believe in the experience of an old man: goblins were involved in this "
"orcish attack."
msgstr ""
"Pero cree en la experiencia de un viejo: los goblins estuvieron involucrados "
"en este ataque orco."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:426
msgid ""
"Anyway, you should ask the other survivors. They might have heard something."
msgstr ""
"De todos modos, deberías preguntar a los otros sobrevivientes. Podrían haber "
"oído algo."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:437
msgid "Can we do anything to help ?"
msgstr "¿Podemos hacer algo para ayudar?"

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:441
msgid ""
"The guardian of Udxatfe must be informed of what happened. But I need all "
"the guards of Zei to defend the city. "
msgstr ""
"El guardián de Udxatfe debe ser informado de lo que pasó. Pero necesito a "
"todos los guardias de Zei para defender la ciudad. "

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:451
msgid ""
"You look like you can defend yourself. I need you to come with me and my men "
"to Udxatfe. Any problem with that?"
msgstr ""
"Parece que puedes defenderte. Necesito que vengas conmigo y mis hombres a "
"Udxatfe. ¿Algún problema con eso?"

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:453
msgid "No, sir. I'm sure your experience will help us reach Udxatfe safely."
msgstr ""
"No, señor. Estoy seguro de que su experiencia nos ayudará a llegar a Udxatfe "
"con seguridad."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:468
msgid ""
"Hey, I’m glad to see there are still courageous young people. Give me five, "
"young boy!"
msgstr "¡Oye, me alegra ver que aún hay jóvenes valientes. ¡Chócala, joven!"

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:472
msgid ""
"It looks like the people you are travelling with are trusting you. I think I "
"will let you lead them, as long as you don't prove them wrong."
msgstr ""
"Parece que la gente con la que viajas confía en ti. Creo que te dejaré "
"liderarlos, siempre que no les demuestres lo contrario."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:485
msgid ""
"Csia is a hero. Heroes, of whom you will soon have a collection, will always "
"be recalled automatically. Heroes can pick up and equip items. Once "
"recruited, they will provide you with an additional unit type to recruit. If "
"a hero dies, you won't be able to recruit this unit type anymore."
msgstr ""
"Csia es un héroe. Los héroes, de los que pronto tendrás una colección, serán "
"siempre reincorporados automáticamente. Los héroes pueden recoger y equipar "
"objetos. Una vez reclutados, te proporcionarán un tipo de unidad adicional "
"para reclutar. Si un héroe muere, no podrás reclutar este tipo de unidad ya."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:491
msgid "You can now recruit sergeants."
msgstr "Ahora puedes reclutar sargentos."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:496
msgid "We can do it by ourselves, sir. The city needs you."
msgstr "Podemos hacerlo solos, señor. La ciudad te necesita."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:500
msgid ""
"Meh, it’s not a bad thing. We need a hero to solve the problems here and "
"those aren’t any of your concern. Good luck!"
msgstr ""
"Meh, no es algo malo. Necesitamos un héroe para resolver los problemas aquí "
"y esos no son de tu incumbencia. ¡Buena suerte!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:508
msgid ""
"My friends, I'm afraid my journey is not over. If I want to avenge Gu, I "
"need to go find Udxatfe's guardian to make sure nothing worse is happening "
"in Idaamub."
msgstr ""
"Mis amigos, temo que mi viaje no ha terminado. Si quiero vengar a Gu, "
"necesito ir a encontrar al guardián de Udxatfe para asegurarme de que nada "
"peor esté pasando en Idaamub."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:512
msgid ""
"But you can't come with me. The farms need to be repaired and the fields to "
"be planted."
msgstr ""
"Pero no pueden venir conmigo. Las granjas necesitan ser reparadas y los "
"campos ser plantados."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:517
msgid ""
"We understand. We will take care of your farm and fields while you're away."
msgstr "Entendemos. Cuidaremos de tu granja y campos mientras estás ausente."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:522
msgid ""
"Had you not been here, we'd surely all be dead by now. It's the least we can "
"do."
msgstr ""
"Si no hubieras estado aquí, seguramente todos estaríamos muertos ya. Es lo "
"mínimo que podemos hacer."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:527
msgid "Here, take this gold. You'll need it more than us for your journey."
msgstr "Aquí, toma este oro. Lo necesitarás más que nosotros para tu viaje."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:535
msgid ""
"Thank you my friends and farewell. I'll come back as soon as I will have "
"avenged Gu."
msgstr "Gracias mis amigos y adiós. Volveré tan pronto como haya vengado a Gu."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:552
msgid "You can no longer recruit nor recall Peasants and Woodsmen."
msgstr "Ya no puedes reclutar ni reincorporar Campesinos y Leñadores."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:556
msgid ""
"Without the Woodsmen, we will have to buy food, and this will cost us gold."
msgstr ""
"Sin los Leñadores, tendremos que comprar comida, y esto nos costará oro."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:561
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/help.cfg:155
msgid ""
"You will lose 1 food at the beginning of each scenario. Bonus scenarios will "
"not cost you food.\n"
"If you have no food, every unit of yours will lose some HP at the beginning "
"of your turns.\n"
"Traders sell food, but you can also loot some on enemies.\n"
"You can check how much food you have by right-clicking anywhere on the map."
msgstr ""
"Perderás 1 comida al inicio de cada escenario. Los escenarios bonus no te "
"costarán comida.\n"
"Si no tienes comida, cada unidad tuya perderá algunos PV al inicio de tus "
"turnos.\n"
"Los comerciantes venden comida, pero también puedes saquear algo en "
"enemigos.\n"
"Puedes verificar cuánta comida tienes haciendo clic derecho en cualquier "
"lugar del mapa."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:571
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/help.cfg:166
msgid ""
"You will lose 1 food at the beginning of each scenario. Bonus scenarios will "
"not cost you food.\n"
"If you have no food, you will not be able to proceed to next scenario.\n"
"Traders sell food, but you can also loot some on enemies.\n"
"You can check how much food you have by right-clicking anywhere on the map."
msgstr ""
"Perderás 1 comida al inicio de cada escenario. Los escenarios bonus no te "
"costarán comida.\n"
"Si no tienes comida, no podrás proceder al siguiente escenario.\n"
"Los comerciantes venden comida, pero también puedes saquear algo en "
"enemigos.\n"
"Puedes verificar cuánta comida tienes haciendo clic derecho en cualquier "
"lugar del mapa."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:592
msgid "I will continue with you."
msgstr "Continuaré contigo."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:596
msgid ""
"Based on what happened in the crypt, I hope to witness things that haven't "
"occurred since the War of Legions."
msgstr ""
"Basado en lo que pasó en la cripta, espero presenciar cosas que no han "
"ocurrido desde la Guerra de Legiones."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:602
msgid "I won't continue with you."
msgstr "No continuaré contigo."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:606
msgid "It is too dangerous out there and I would only be a burden."
msgstr "Es demasiado peligroso allá afuera y solo sería una carga."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:610
msgid "I will pray for you saving us all."
msgstr "Rezaré por ti salvándonos a todos."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:634
msgid "You can no longer recruit nor recall Initiates."
msgstr "Ya no puedes reclutar ni reincorporar Iniciados."

#. [message], speaker=Addthynec
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:668
msgid ""
"You're the first farmer to come to our mill since the orcs began their "
"horrible massacre."
msgstr ""
"Eres el primer granjero en venir a nuestro molino desde que los orcos "
"comenzaron su horrible masacre."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:672
msgid "I'm sorry, but we're not here to mill grain."
msgstr "Lo siento, pero no estamos aquí para moler grano."

#. [message], speaker=Addthynec
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:676
msgid ""
"You didn't come to have your grain milled? If the orcs went all the way to "
"the Arable Highlands, horribly savage days await us."
msgstr ""
"¿No viniste a moler tu grano? Si los orcos fueron hasta las Tierras Altas "
"Arables, días horriblemente salvajes nos esperan."

#. [message], speaker=Addthynec
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:680
msgid ""
"They emptied our granary, and then cut down the supply chain. We will only "
"have enough food for a week, best case."
msgstr ""
"Vaciaron nuestro granero, y luego cortaron la cadena de suministro. Solo "
"tendremos suficiente comida para una semana, en el mejor caso."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:684
msgid "Can we do something to help you?"
msgstr "¿Podemos hacer algo para ayudarte?"

#. [message], speaker=Addthynec
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:688
msgid ""
"I wanted to go to the beach to fish, but it seems the orcs left behind some "
"of those horrible mudcrawlers."
msgstr ""
"Quería ir a la playa a pescar, pero parece que los orcos dejaron atrás "
"algunos de esos horribles rastreadores de lodo."

#. [message], speaker=Addthynec
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:692
msgid ""
"I begged the captain of the guard to help us clean the beach, but he doesn't "
"realize the seriousness of the situation. He won't reassign the guards on "
"duty at the doors until they have been repaired."
msgstr ""
"Supliqué al capitán de la guardia que nos ayudara a limpiar la playa, pero "
"no se da cuenta de la seriedad de la situación. No reasignará a los guardias "
"en servicio en las puertas hasta que hayan sido reparadas."

#. [message], speaker=Addthynec
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:696
msgid ""
"If you are brave enough to clean the beach (what I'm not capable of), it "
"would greatly help the citizens."
msgstr ""
"Si eres lo suficientemente valiente para limpiar la playa (lo que yo no soy "
"capaz), ayudaría mucho a los ciudadanos."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:706
msgid "Well, actually, we already got rid of them"
msgstr "Bueno, de hecho, ya nos deshicimos de ellos"

#. [message], speaker=Addthynec
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:711
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:756
msgid "Thank you so much. Now we won't starve to death."
msgstr "Muchas gracias. Ahora no moriremos de hambre."

#. [message], speaker=Addthynec
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:715
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:760
msgid ""
"Please take some food as a mark of appreciation. We don't need to spare it "
"as much now, thanks to you."
msgstr ""
"Por favor toma algo de comida como muestra de aprecio. No necesitamos "
"ahorrarla tanto ahora, gracias a ti."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:720
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:765
msgid "You receive 5 food."
msgstr "Recibes 5 comida."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:729
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1552
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2306
msgid "We will see what we can do."
msgstr "Veremos qué podemos hacer."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:751
msgid ""
"That's it. We killed the mudcrawlers that were on the beach. You can fish "
"now."
msgstr ""
"Eso es. Matamos a los rastreadores de lodo que estaban en la playa. Puedes "
"pescar ahora."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:781
msgid "Excuse me. You look in bad shape. What happened to you?"
msgstr "Disculpe. Pareces en mal estado. ¿Qué te pasó?"

#. [message], speaker=Tiddin
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:785
msgid ""
"The orcs set my house on fire. The crooks who teach the orcs how to raise "
"skeletons and set fire to brave people's houses deserve Emiijainu's torture."
msgstr ""
"Los orcos incendiaron mi casa. Los estafadores que enseñan a los orcos cómo "
"levantar esqueletos e incendiar las casas de la gente valiente merecen la "
"tortura de Emiijainu."

#. [message], speaker=Tiddin
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:789
msgid ""
"As if their strike force was not devastating enough, those damned orcs "
"brought those horrible monsters from the highlands."
msgstr ""
"Como si su fuerza de ataque no fuera lo suficientemente devastadora, esos "
"malditos orcos trajeron esos horribles monstruos de las tierras altas."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:793
msgid "Can we do something for you?"
msgstr "¿Podemos hacer algo por ti?"

#. [message], speaker=Tiddin
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:797
msgid ""
"You can't unburn my house, but if you could find the orcs and give them a "
"taste of their own medicine, that would be nice."
msgstr ""
"No puedes desquemar mi casa, pero si pudieras encontrar a los orcos y darles "
"una probadita de su propia medicina, sería genial."

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:811
msgid ""
"You're safe here for now: I think we left a bitter taste in orc's mouths "
"after the slaughter they suffered last night."
msgstr ""
"Estás seguro aquí por ahora: creo que dejamos un sabor amargo en la boca de "
"los orcos después de la matanza que sufrieron anoche."

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:861
msgid ""
"Welcome to the Black Hammer Forge. Orcs nearly stole everything from us but, "
"what's left, you won't find anywhere at a better price. What can I do for "
"you today?"
msgstr ""
"Bienvenido a la Forja del Martillo Negro. Los orcos casi nos robaron todo, "
"pero, lo que queda, no lo encontrarás en ningún lugar a mejor precio. ¿Qué "
"puedo hacer por ti hoy?"

