#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1366
msgid ""
"South: Crypt of the Sacred Blood\n"
"                        North: Qyizu, Udxatfe"
msgstr ""
"Sur: Cripta de la Sangre Sagrada\n"
"                        Norte: Qyizu, Udxatfe"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1395
msgid "Excuse me, what happened here?"
msgstr "Disculpe, ¿qué pasó aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Lercoc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1399
msgid ""
"The orcs broke into my house while I was sleeping. They destroyed everything "
"that wasn't looking like a magical object and stole the rest. It was "
"terrible!"
msgstr ""
"Los orcos irrumpieron en mi casa mientras dormía. Destruyeron todo que no "
"parecía un objeto mágico y robaron el resto. ¡Fue terrible!"

#. [message], speaker=Lercoc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1403
msgid ""
"I can't understand why the orcs imagined they would find magical artifacts "
"in Zei."
msgstr ""
"No puedo entender por qué los orcos imaginaron que encontrarían artefactos "
"mágicos en Zei."

#. [message], speaker=Lercoc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1411
msgid "Some forks and rakes don't justify Zei begin brought to the Emiijainu."
msgstr ""
"Algunos tenedores y rastrillos no justifican que Zei sea llevado al "
"Emiijainu."

#. [message], speaker=Lercoc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1415
msgid ""
"It looked like the orcs followed the orders of someone named Isut. ''Isut "
"says we must set fire!'', ''Isut says we must destroy everything!''."
msgstr ""
"Parecía que los orcos seguían las órdenes de alguien llamado Isut. «¡Isut "
"dice que debemos incendiar!», «¡Isut dice que debemos destruir todo!»."

#. [message], speaker=Lercoc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1419
msgid ""
"If I find who that Isut is, I might actually set fire and destroy everything."
msgstr "Si encuentro quién es ese Isut, podría incendiar y destruir todo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1423
msgid "Finding this Isut might indeed bring some answers."
msgstr "Encontrar a este Isut podría traer algunas respuestas."

#. [message], speaker=Soranyc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1443
msgid ""
"Orcs... If you want my opinion, we should have chased them from the hills "
"when we settled there."
msgstr ""
"Orcos... Si quieres mi opinión, deberíamos haberlos expulsado de las colinas "
"cuando nos establecimos allí."

#. [message], speaker=Soranyc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1447
msgid ""
"Those dung eaters only left me two mules and a lame mare. I can sell the "
"mules, but it won't reimburse the price they cost me. I can sell it to you "
"for 320 gold."
msgstr ""
"Esos comedores de estiércol solo me dejaron dos mulas y una yegua coja. "
"Puedo vender las mulas, pero no reembolsará el precio que me costaron. Puedo "
"vendértela a ti por 320 de oro."

#. [message], speaker=Soranyc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1451
msgid "Do you need one?"
msgstr "¿Necesitas una?"

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1453
msgid "I'm sorry but we don't."
msgstr "Lo siento pero no."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1465
msgid "Actually, it would be quite useful to carry the food."
msgstr "De hecho, sería bastante útil para llevar la comida."

#. [message], speaker=Soranyc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1479
msgid "I am sorry, but we don't have that much money."
msgstr "Lo siento, pero no tenemos tanto dinero."

#. [unit], id=Flame, type=Bay Horse
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1490
msgid "Flame"
msgstr "Flame"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1498
msgid "Here is. What's her name?"
msgstr "Aquí está. ¿Cuál es su nombre?"

#. [message], speaker=Soranyc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1502
msgid "She is Flame. But don't think she will listen if you call her."
msgstr "Es Flame. Pero no pienses que escuchará si la llamas."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1524
msgid "Was this your house?"
msgstr "¿Era esta tu casa?"

#. [message], speaker=Aldrsil
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1528
msgid ""
"Yes it was. I was stationed at the northern watchtower when the orcs began "
"attacking in waves."
msgstr ""
"Sí lo era. Estaba estacionado en la torre de vigilancia norte cuando los "
"orcos comenzaron a atacar en olas."

#. [message], speaker=Aldrsil
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1532
msgid ""
"If I weren't that dumb, I could have been back on time and prevent them from "
"burning my house. They have surely invaded the tower by now."
msgstr ""
"Si no fuera tan tonto, podría haber regresado a tiempo y evitar que quemaran "
"mi casa. Seguramente ya invadieron la torre."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1536
msgid "Isn't that really bad news?"
msgstr "¿No es eso realmente una mala noticia?"

#. [message], speaker=Aldrsil
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1540
msgid ""
"It could be worse. They may not have already succeeded in understanding the "
"mechanism to enter the arsenal. The idea that the rest of our weapons may "
"fall in the hands of the orcs breaks my heart."
msgstr ""
"Podría ser peor. Puede que no hayan logrado entender el mecanismo para "
"entrar al arsenal. La idea de que el resto de nuestras armas pueda caer en "
"manos de los orcos me rompe el corazón."

#. [message], speaker=Aldrsil
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1544
msgid "If you think you can match up, don't hesitate. Step in!"
msgstr "Si crees que puedes igualarlos, no dudes. ¡Entra!"

#. [message], speaker=Aldrsil
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1548
msgid ""
"Once I will have saved everything I can in my house, I will go back to the "
"tower."
msgstr ""
"Una vez que haya salvado todo lo que pueda en mi casa, volveré a la torre."

#. [message], speaker=Gloraevan
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1568
msgid ""
"We really are overreacting to the orcs. OK, they made a huge mess but "
"there's no reasons for looking too far: greed is their only motivation."
msgstr ""
"Realmente estamos exagerando con los orcos. OK, hicieron un gran desastre "
"pero no hay razones para mirar demasiado lejos: la avaricia es su única "
"motivación."

#. [message], speaker=Gloraevan
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1572
msgid ""
"They only wanted quality weapons, same as you. By the way, my son Denogyc "
"should be able to replace the stuff you lost."
msgstr ""
"Solo querían armas de calidad, igual que tú. Por cierto, mi hijo Denogyc "
"debería poder reemplazar las cosas que perdiste."

#. [message], speaker=Gloraevan
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1576
msgid "See with him inside!"
msgstr "¡Míralo con él adentro!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1580
msgid "We will."
msgstr "Lo haremos."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1594
msgid "Are you OK?"
msgstr "¿Estás bien?"

#. [message], speaker=Owreddoc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1598
msgid ""
"The attack of last night has been terrible! I nearly died. But I'm fine now."
msgstr ""
"¡El ataque de anoche ha sido terrible! Casi muero. Pero estoy bien ahora."

#. [message], speaker=Owreddoc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1602
msgid ""
"When my sister will know what the orcs did to us, she will be furious! But "
"she may worry about me."
msgstr ""
"Cuando mi hermana sepa lo que los orcos nos hicieron, ¡estará furiosa! Pero "
"podría preocuparse por mí."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1606
msgid "Where is she?"
msgstr "¿Dónde está?"

#. [message], speaker=Owreddoc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1610
msgid ""
"She is bowman in the legion, stationed at Udxatfe. If you go in that "
"direction, can you please tell her I'm fine?"
msgstr ""
"Es arquera en la legión, estacionada en Udxatfe. Si van en esa dirección, "
"¿pueden decirle que estoy bien?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1614
msgid "We will do what we can."
msgstr "Haremos lo que podamos."

#. [message], speaker=Owreddoc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1618
msgid ""
"I'm sure you won't regret it: her name is Roiwv. I hope she don't worry "
"about me."
msgstr ""
"Estoy seguro de que no se arrepentirán: su nombre es Roiwv. Espero que no se "
"preocupe por mí."

#. [message], speaker=Siok
#. [message], speaker=Is
#. [message], speaker=Uwiu
#. [message], speaker=Asaem
#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#. [message], speaker=narrator
#. [message], speaker=Ubidaiubua
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1649
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1980
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:998
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1172
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1788
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1023
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/38_Isut.cfg:728
msgid "Hello."
msgstr "Hola."

#. [message], speaker=Siok
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1655
msgid "I'm Siok the fencer, or rather Siok the failure, those times."
msgstr ""
"Soy Siok el esgrimidor, o mejor dicho Siok el fracaso, en estos tiempos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1659
msgid "Why do you say that?"
msgstr "¿Por qué dices eso?"

#. [message], speaker=Siok
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1663
msgid ""
"I was told I missed by little the most interesting thing to ever happened in "
"this damned village."
msgstr ""
"Me dijeron que me perdí por poco la cosa más interesante que jamás ha pasado "
"en esta maldita aldea."

#. [message], speaker=Siok
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1667
msgid ""
"If you need a fencer, take me with you! I would like to have some fun for "
"once in this kingdom."
msgstr ""
"Si necesitas un esgrimidor, ¡llévame contigo! Me gustaría divertirme por una "
"vez en este reino."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1678
msgid ""
"We are looking for some people to strengthen our group. Are you interested?"
msgstr ""
"¿Buscamos algunas personas para fortalecer nuestro grupo? ¿Estás interesado?"

#. [message], speaker=Siok
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1686
msgid ""
"Usually, I sell my services for quite a price, but I'm ready to ask for less "
"to leave this dump."
msgstr ""
"Usualmente, vendo mis servicios por un precio bastante alto, pero estoy "
"listo para pedir menos para dejar este basurero."

#. [message], speaker=Siok
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1690
msgid "Does 450 gold suit you?"
msgstr "¿Te parece bien 450 de oro?"

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1692
msgid "Yes, come with us."
msgstr "Sí, ven con nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Siok
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1702
msgid "I see good luck won't head my way. You have no gold my friend."
msgstr "Veo que la buena suerte no vendrá hacia mí. No tienes oro amigo mío."

#. [message], speaker=Siok
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1706
msgid ""
"Come back when your purse will be full enough. I can't allow myself to do "
"all this for free."
msgstr ""
"Vuelve cuando tu bolsa esté lo suficientemente llena. No puedo permitirme "
"hacer todo esto gratis."

#. [message], speaker=Siok
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1727
msgid "Finally salvation. Let's see what problems still await us."
msgstr "Finalmente salvación. Veamos qué problemas aún nos esperan."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1740
msgid ""
"Siok is a hero. Heroes, of whom you will soon have a collection, will always "
"be recalled automatically. Heroes can pick up and equip items. Once "
"recruited, they will provide you with an additional unit type to recruit. If "
"a hero dies, you won't be able to recruit this unit type anymore."
msgstr ""
"Siok es un héroe. Los héroes, de los que pronto tendrás una colección, serán "
"siempre reincorporados automáticamente. Los héroes pueden recoger y equipar "
"objetos. Una vez reclutados, te proporcionarán un tipo de unidad adicional "
"para reclutar. Si un héroe muere, no podrás reclutar este tipo de unidad ya."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1746
msgid "You can now recruit Fencers."
msgstr "Ahora puedes reclutar Esgrimidores."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1753
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2102
msgid "Sorry, we can't give you that much gold."
msgstr "Lo siento, no podemos darte tanto oro."

#. [message], speaker=Siok
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1757
msgid "Great! Condemn me to stay here."
msgstr "¡Genial! Condéname a quedarme aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Siok
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1761
msgid ""
"I will go annoy the cows in the fields... I heard there is not much else to "
"do here."
msgstr ""
"Iré a molestar a las vacas en los campos... Escuché que no hay mucho más que "
"hacer aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1791
msgid "Hello, barman. What do you have to sell?"
msgstr "Hola, cantinero. ¿Qué tienes para vender?"

#. [message], speaker=Vygwynyc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1795
msgid ""
"I'm sorry but since the orcish attack, we have nearly nothing left to sell."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento pero desde el ataque orco, casi no nos queda nada para vender."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1799
msgid "What a shame."
msgstr "Qué lástima."

#. [message], speaker=Vygwynyc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1803
msgid ""
"Who knows what those creatures from hell were thinking they would find at "
"Uteaqniq's Roost. At least, they didn't stay long."
msgstr ""
"Quién sabe qué pensaban esas criaturas del infierno que encontrarían en el "
"Nido de Uteaqniq. Al menos, no se quedaron mucho tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1807
msgid "I hope you will be able to reopen soon."
msgstr "Espero que puedas reabrir pronto."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1827
msgid ""
"We would need to buy some food to continue our journey. Could you sell us "
"some?"
msgstr ""
"Necesitaríamos comprar algo de comida para continuar nuestro viaje. ¿Podrías "
"vendernos algo?"

#. [message], speaker=Vygwynyc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1843
msgid ""
"I don't have much left, but I don't want you to starve during your journey "
"either."
msgstr ""
"No me queda mucho, pero tampoco quiero que mueras de hambre durante tu viaje."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1845
msgid "Buy 1 food for $food_price| gold"
msgstr "Comprar 1 comida por $food_price| de oro"

#. [message], speaker=Vygwynyc
#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [message], speaker=Aenyc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1855
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1883
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1911
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1909
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1945
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1981
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:705
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:733
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:761
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1235
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1271
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1307
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1632
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1668
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1704
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1934
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1970
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:2006
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1813
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1849
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1885
msgid "You don't have enough money."
msgstr "No tienes suficiente dinero."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1866
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1894
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1922
msgid "We now have $food_counter| food."
msgstr "Ahora tenemos $food_counter| comida."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1873
msgid "Buy 5 food for $(5*$food_price) gold"
msgstr "Comprar 5 comida por $(5*$food_price) de oro"

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1901
msgid "Buy 10 food for $(10*$food_price) gold"
msgstr "Comprar 10 comida por $(10*$food_price) de oro"

#. [message], speaker=Vygwynyc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1937
msgid "Do you have something to transport it?"
msgstr "¿Tienes algo para transportarla?"

#. [message], speaker=Vygwynyc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1945
msgid "Come back when you do then."
msgstr "Vuelve cuando lo tengas entonces."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1982
msgid "You look injured. What happened to you?"
msgstr "Pareces herido. ¿Qué te pasó?"

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1986
msgid ""
"Sorry for not being very presentable. I got hit by an arrow last night but "
"it's only a scratch."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento por no estar muy presentable. Me alcanzó una flecha anoche pero es "
"solo un rasguño."

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:1990
msgid ""
"But I'm ready to go back to the fight, if someone finally believes in me."
msgstr ""
"Pero estoy listo para volver a la lucha, si alguien finalmente cree en mí."

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2005
msgid "I'm Is, the bowwoman. If your need a good bowman, don't look further."
msgstr "Soy Is, la arquera. Si necesitas un buen arquero, no busques más."

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2020
msgid "Gaelyn fixed me after I was injured defending the village."
msgstr "Gaelyn me arregló después de que me hirieran defendiendo la aldea."

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2031
msgid "Can we help you with something?"
msgstr "¿Podemos ayudarte con algo?"

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2039
msgid ""
"I need 525 gold to pay Gaelyn. If you help me with that, I will come fight "
"with you."
msgstr ""
"Necesito 525 de oro para pagar a Gaelyn. Si me ayudas con eso, iré a luchar "
"contigo."

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2043
msgid "Are you interested?"
msgstr "¿Estás interesado?"

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2045
msgid "Sure, here is the gold."
msgstr "Claro, aquí está el oro."

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2070
msgid ""
"At your service. Just tell me where we go, and I will do what I can so that "
"we arrive there alive."
msgstr ""
"A tu servicio. Solo dime a dónde vamos, y haré lo que pueda para que "
"lleguemos allí vivos."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2083
msgid ""
"Is is a hero. Heroes, of whom you will soon have a collection, will always "
"be recalled automatically. Heroes can pick up and equip items. Once "
"recruited, they will provide you with an additional unit type to recruit. If "
"a hero dies, you won't be able to recruit this unit type anymore."
msgstr ""
"Is es un héroe. Los héroes, de los que pronto tendrás una colección, serán "
"siempre reincorporados automáticamente. Los héroes pueden recoger y equipar "
"objetos. Una vez reclutados, te proporcionarán un tipo de unidad adicional "
"para reclutar. Si un héroe muere, no podrás reclutar este tipo de unidad ya."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2089
msgid "You can now recruit bowmen."
msgstr "Ahora puedes reclutar arqueros."

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2095
msgid ""
"I appreciate the trust you place in me, but I need to pay my debts before "
"everything. Come back when you have the gold."
msgstr ""
"Aprecio la confianza que depositas en mí, pero necesito pagar mis deudas "
"antes de todo. Vuelve cuando tengas el oro."

#. [message], speaker=Is
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2106
msgid ""
"You never know, right? If you change your mind, you know where to find me."
msgstr ""
"Nunca se sabe, ¿verdad? Si cambias de opinión, sabes dónde encontrarme."

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2161
msgid ""
"The divine fire is in you my child. Your destiny might incline you to "
"accomplish great things, but let's begin by dealing with the most urgent "
"matters first."
msgstr ""
"El fuego divino está en ti hijo mío. Tu destino podría inclinarte a realizar "
"grandes cosas, pero comencemos por lidiar con los asuntos más urgentes "
"primero."

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2176
msgid ""
"If you need potions, I can sell you useful ones and at low price. Do you "
"want to see them?"
msgstr ""
"Si necesitas pociones, puedo venderte útiles y a bajo precio. ¿Quieres "
"verlas?"

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2178
msgid "Buy books"
msgstr "Comprar libros"

#. [option]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2189
msgid "Buy potions"
msgstr "Comprar pociones"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2224
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1830
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1541
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1153
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1549
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1852
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1731
msgid "What kind of book do you want to buy?"
msgstr "¿Qué tipo de libro quieres comprar?"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2225
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1546
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:3970
msgid "Deadly spear"
msgstr "Lanza mortal"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2226
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:4003
msgid "Weakening enemies"
msgstr "Debilitando enemigos"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2227
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:4019
msgid "Fireball burst"
msgstr "Explosión de bola de fuego"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2228
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1835
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:4155
msgid "Sparkles"
msgstr "Chispas"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2229
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:4056
msgid "Explosive powder"
msgstr "Polvo explosivo"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2230
msgid "The Philosopher's Stone"
msgstr "La Piedra Filosofal"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2231
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:4207
msgid "Healing hands"
msgstr "Manos sanadoras"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2257
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1861
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1572
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1184
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1580
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1883
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:1762
msgid "What kind of potion do you want to buy?"
msgstr "¿Qué tipo de poción quieres comprar?"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2258
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1863
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1576
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1188
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1585
msgid "Small experience potion"
msgstr "Poción pequeña de experiencia"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2259
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1862
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/17_Udxatfe.cfg:1577
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:1189
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/28_Travelers.cfg:1586
msgid "Small healing potion"
msgstr "Poción pequeña de sanación"

#. [message], speaker=Marogin
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2302
msgid ""
"If you go north, know that only orcs come back from this direction since "
"last night's attack. If you wipe out the scum prowling around Qyizu's pass, "
"it will be far easier for us to make the road safe when the captain will "
"order us."
msgstr ""
"Si vas al norte, sabe que solo orcos regresan de esta dirección desde el "
"ataque de anoche. Si eliminas la escoria merodeando alrededor del paso de "
"Qyizu, será mucho más fácil para nosotros hacer el camino seguro cuando el "
"capitán nos ordene."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2337
msgid ""
"I think we are done with Zei. I would rather go back to the Arable "
"Highlands, but the kingdom needs us."
msgstr ""
"Creo que terminamos con Zei. Preferiría volver a las Tierras Altas Arables, "
"pero el reino nos necesita."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2353
msgid "We don't have enough food to continue our journey."
msgstr "No tenemos suficiente comida para continuar nuestro viaje."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2370
msgid "We don't have anything to transport our food."
msgstr "No tenemos nada para transportar nuestra comida."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/06_Zei.cfg:2396
msgid "The inhabitants should be able to fish now."
msgstr "Los habitantes deberían poder pescar ahora."

#. [scenario], id=07_Yooradweak_s_pass
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:4
msgid "Yooradweak's pass"
msgstr "Paso de Yooradweak"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:41
msgid "Get to the other side of Yooradweak's pass"
msgstr "Llega al otro lado del paso de Yooradweak"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:57
msgid "Clear Yooradweak's pass"
msgstr "Despeja el paso de Yooradweak"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:73
msgid "Find another way to Udxatfe"
msgstr "Encuentra otra forma de llegar a Udxatfe"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:95
msgid "Find the entrance of Uvju's cross"
msgstr "Encuentra la entrada de la cruz de Uvju"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:124
msgid "Free the northern watchtower before completing the main objective"
msgstr ""
"Libera la torre de vigilancia norte antes de completar el objetivo principal"

#. [side], type=Spearman
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:306
msgid "Ofcuu"
msgstr "Ofcuu"

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:359
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:373
msgid ""
"Our next stop is Udxatfe. We need to tell the guardian about what happened "
"here in Zei."
msgstr ""
"Nuestra próxima parada es Udxatfe. Necesitamos decirle al guardián sobre lo "
"que pasó aquí en Zei."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:363
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:377
msgid ""
"He will surely be able to draw more information with his knowledge than we "
"with ours."
msgstr ""
"Seguramente podrá obtener más información con su conocimiento que nosotros "
"con el nuestro."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:367
msgid ""
"The shortest way is to go west through Yooradweak's pass then through "
"Qyizu's mines"
msgstr ""
"El camino más corto es ir al oeste a través del paso de Yooradweak y luego a "
"través de las minas de Qyizu"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:381
msgid ""
"From what I know, the shortest way is to go west through Yooradweak's pass."
msgstr ""
"Por lo que sé, el camino más corto es ir al oeste a través del paso de "
"Yooradweak."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:394
msgid ""
"We must expect to encounter orcish resistance there. Clearing the pass will "
"benefit us but also the people of Zei."
msgstr ""
"Debemos esperar encontrar resistencia orca allí. Despejar el paso nos "
"beneficiará pero también a la gente de Zei."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:411
msgid "Uvju's cross"
msgstr "Cruz de Uvju"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:446
msgid ""
"North: Uvju's cross\n"
"West: Zei\n"
"East: Qyizu, Udxatfe"
msgstr ""
"Norte: Cruz de Uvju\n"
"Oeste: Zei\n"
"Este: Qyizu, Udxatfe"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:600
msgid "The doors are closed. Let's try to open them."
msgstr "Las puertas están cerradas. Intentemos abrirlas."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:619
msgid ""
"I can't open it. It looks like someone has stacked rocks on the other side "
"of the door."
msgstr ""
"No puedo abrirla. Parece que alguien ha apilado rocas al otro lado de la "
"puerta."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:623
msgid "I don't know if orcs or humans did it, but we can't use the pass."
msgstr "No sé si orcos o humanos lo hicieron, pero no podemos usar el paso."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:627
msgid "We need to find another way to reach Udxatfe."
msgstr "Necesitamos encontrar otra forma de llegar a Udxatfe."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:637
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:660
msgid "There is a way."
msgstr "Hay una forma."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:641
msgid ""
"A tunnel run through the mountain. It begins in Uvju's cross and end on the "
"other side of the pass."
msgstr ""
"Un túnel atraviesa la montaña. Comienza en la cruz de Uvju y termina al otro "
"lado del paso."

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:645
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:668
msgid "But this is a dark way, full of horrors from the War of Legions."
msgstr ""
"Pero este es un camino oscuro, lleno de horrores de la Guerra de Legiones."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:664
msgid ""
"I've read that a tunnel run through the mountain. It begins in Uvju's cross "
"and end on the other side of the pass."
msgstr ""
"He leído que un túnel atraviesa la montaña. Comienza en la cruz de Uvju y "
"termina al otro lado del paso."

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:692
msgid "I’m glad to see another human."
msgstr "Me alegra ver a otro humano."

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:714
msgid ""
"My troops and I tried to flee from the orcs when they invaded Qyizu, but "
"Zei’s road being blocked, our only option was to go through Uvju’s cross."
msgstr ""
"Mis tropas y yo intentamos huir de los orcos cuando invadieron Qyizu, pero "
"el camino de Zei estando bloqueado, nuestra única opción era ir a través de "
"la cruz de Uvju."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:718
msgid "This is not..."
msgstr "Esto no es..."

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:722
msgid ""
"What a monumental mistake we made there. We had made half the way when those "
"eight-legged monsters began coming in bulk out of the tunnels."
msgstr ""
"Qué error monumental cometimos allí. Habíamos hecho la mitad del camino "
"cuando esos monstruos de ocho patas comenzaron a salir en masa de los "
"túneles."

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:726
msgid "We took to our heels, but… "
msgstr "Huimos, pero… "

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:730
msgid "But… "
msgstr "Pero… "

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:734
msgid "But what?"
msgstr "¿Pero qué?"

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:738
msgid "My God! How deafening were their screams."
msgstr "¡Dios mío! ¡Qué ensordecedores eran sus gritos."

#. [message], speaker=Ofcuu
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:742
msgid "Why does this happen to me? Why?"
msgstr "¿Por qué me pasa esto a mí? ¿Por qué?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:746
msgid ""
"I don't think we will get more info from him. What happened in there seems "
"to have broken his mind."
msgstr ""
"No creo que obtengamos más información de él. Lo que pasó allí parece haber "
"roto su mente."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:769
msgid "I think I found Aldrsil's axe."
msgstr "Creo que encontré el hacha de Aldrsil."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:805
msgid ""
"If we had any other choice, I would rather us not have to pass through "
"Uvju's cross, especially after what Ofcuu told us."
msgstr ""
"Si tuviéramos otra opción, preferiría no tener que pasar por la cruz de "
"Uvju, especialmente después de lo que nos dijo Ofcuu."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:809
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, the pass is blocked, and we have to warn the guardian of "
"Udxatfe."
msgstr ""
"Desafortunadamente, el paso está bloqueado, y tenemos que advertir al "
"guardián de Udxatfe."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:813
msgid "Let's enter the tunnels but be careful everyone."
msgstr "Entremos a los túneles pero sean cuidadosos todos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:923
msgid ""
"There are too many orcs between us and Udxatfe. How are we supposed to get "
"there?"
msgstr ""
"Hay demasiados orcos entre nosotros y Udxatfe. ¿Cómo se supone que lleguemos "
"allí?"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:941
msgid ""
"The pass is blocked. There is no way we will be able to reach Udxatfe and "
"warn the guardian."
msgstr ""
"El paso está bloqueado. No hay forma de que podamos llegar a Udxatfe y "
"advertir al guardián."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/07_Yooradweak_s_pass.cfg:959
msgid ""
"If trained men weren't able to go through Uvju's cross, how could we? We are "
"barely able to kill some orcs."
msgstr ""
"Si hombres entrenados no pudieron pasar por la cruz de Uvju, ¿cómo "
"podríamos? Somos apenas capaces de matar algunos orcos."

#. [scenario], id=08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:4
msgid "Inside Uvju's cross"
msgstr "Dentro de la cruz de Uvju"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:38
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/09_Spider_Maze.cfg:31
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:41
msgid "Find the exit of Uvju's cross"
msgstr "Encuentra la salida de la cruz de Uvju"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:43
msgid "Defeat the enemy leader before exiting"
msgstr "Derrota al líder enemigo antes de salir"

#. [side], type=Monstrosity LotI
#. [side], type=Skeleton Archer
#. [side], type=Ancient Lich
#. [side], type=Deathlord LotI
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:98
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/09_Spider_Maze.cfg:80
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:89
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/37_Old_Temple.cfg:80
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/38_Isut.cfg:110
msgid "Undead"
msgstr "No-muertos"

#. [side], type=Spiderling LoI
#. [side], type=Young Giant Spider
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:437
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/09_Spider_Maze.cfg:270
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:401
msgid "Spiders"
msgstr "Arañas"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:643
msgid "So, here is the famous Uvju's cross."
msgstr "Así que, aquí está la famosa cruz de Uvju."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:647
msgid "Well, it doesn't look nice anyway. Even without what Ofcuu told us."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, no parece bonito de todos modos. Incluso sin lo que nos dijo Ofcuu."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:651
msgid ""
"However, it is the only way to reach Qyizu now that Yooradweak's pass is "
"blocked. I hope no one is afraid of spiders because I can already hear them."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, es la única forma de llegar a Qyizu ahora que el paso de "
"Yooradweak está bloqueado. Espero que nadie tenga miedo a las arañas porque "
"ya las puedo oír."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:664
msgid ""
"This must be the spiders the demons left. It's impressive that they are "
"still here."
msgstr ""
"Estas deben ser las arañas que dejaron los demonios. Es impresionante que "
"aún estén aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:668
msgid "But not really reassuring."
msgstr "Pero no realmente tranquilizador."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:862
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:968
msgid "There are spiders coming out of the pits!"
msgstr "¡Hay arañas saliendo de los pozos!"

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:891
msgid "I would love to study them were they not trying to kill us."
msgstr "Me encantaría estudiarlas si no intentaran matarnos."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:912
msgid "There are spiders coming out of the pits and traps!"
msgstr "¡Hay arañas saliendo de los pozos y trampas!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1103
msgid "The books on the shelf are badly damaged."
msgstr "Los libros en el estante están muy dañados."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1107
msgid "Wait! I found one that should be readable!"
msgstr "¡Espera! ¡Encontré uno que debería ser legible!"

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1126
msgid "Awesome! Give it to me!"
msgstr "¡Genial! ¡Dámelo!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1148
msgid "The are more mold than paper on this shelf."
msgstr "Hay más moho que papel en este estante."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1152
msgid ""
"It looks like one of the books has not been completely eaten by the mold."
msgstr ""
"Parece que uno de los libros no ha sido completamente comido por el moho."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1171
msgid "Don't touch it! Let me treat it with the care it deserves."
msgstr "¡No lo toques! Déjame tratarlo con el cuidado que merece."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1190
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/09_Spider_Maze.cfg:565
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:482
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:532
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:665
msgid "There are spiders coming out of the traps!"
msgstr "¡Hay arañas saliendo de las trampas!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1267
msgid "A frightening lot of spiders!"
msgstr "¡Un montón aterrador de arañas!"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1333
msgid "Damned orcs! It looks like they have raised undead here too."
msgstr "¡Malditos orcos! Parece que han levantado no-muertos aquí también."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1337
msgid ""
"If we can find the undead leader and defeat it, it will be easier to exit."
msgstr ""
"Si podemos encontrar al líder no-muerto y derrotarlo, será más fácil salir."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1361
msgid "Come over here! I think I found something."
msgstr "¡Ven aquí! Creo que encontré algo."

#. [message]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1381
msgid "It looks like an elevator. We could use it to go back to the surface."
msgstr "Parece un elevador. Podríamos usarlo para volver a la superficie."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1391
msgid "Except that I can't see any light when I look up."
msgstr "Excepto que no veo ninguna luz cuando miro arriba."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1397
msgid "I don't think so... I can't see any light when I look up."
msgstr "No lo creo... No veo ninguna luz cuando miro arriba."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1403
msgid "I don't see any other path. We must take it and see where it leads to."
msgstr "No veo otro camino. Debemos tomarlo y ver a dónde lleva."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1425
msgid "Let's go down. I hope the exit is down there and spiders are not."
msgstr "Bajemos. Espero que la salida esté abajo y las arañas no."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1453
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/09_Spider_Maze.cfg:843
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:1017
msgid "Wait for us! We are still fighting the spiders here!"
msgstr "¡Espérennos! ¡Aún estamos luchando contra las arañas aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1482
msgid "My God! The screams! They are deafening!"
msgstr "¡Dios mío! ¡Los gritos! ¡Son ensordecedores!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/08_Inside_Uvju_s_cross.cfg:1486
msgid "Why is this happening to us? Why?"
msgstr "¿Por qué nos pasa esto? ¿Por qué?"

#. [scenario], id=09_Spider_Maze
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/09_Spider_Maze.cfg:4
msgid "Spider Maze"
msgstr "Laberinto de Arañas"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/09_Spider_Maze.cfg:36
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:46
msgid "Kill all spiders"
msgstr "Mata a todas las arañas"

#. [message]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/09_Spider_Maze.cfg:523
msgid ""
"I'm afraid we will have to deal with spiders down here too. Probably undead "
"also."
msgstr ""
"Temo que tendremos que lidiar con arañas aquí abajo también. Probablemente "
"no-muertos también."

#. [message], speaker=Lujeje
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/09_Spider_Maze.cfg:536
msgid ""
"It would be a good thing if we were able to get rid of the spiders. That "
"would allow scholars to study that ruin."
msgstr ""
"Sería algo bueno si pudiéramos deshacernos de las arañas. Eso permitiría a "
"los eruditos estudiar esa ruina."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/09_Spider_Maze.cfg:542
msgid ""
"It would be a good thing if we were able to get rid of the spiders. Not that "
"it would become a popular place, but still."
msgstr ""
"Sería algo bueno si pudiéramos deshacernos de las arañas. No es que se "
"convierta en un lugar popular, pero aun así."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/09_Spider_Maze.cfg:548
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, I'm not sure we have the time to do this. Our main mission "
"remains to warn the guardian."
msgstr ""
"Desafortunadamente, no estoy seguro de que tengamos el tiempo para hacer "
"esto. Nuestra misión principal sigue siendo advertir al guardián."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/09_Spider_Maze.cfg:831
msgid ""
"We have not killed all the spiders before us, but the mission is more "
"important. Let's proceed to this new room."
msgstr ""
"No hemos matado a todas las arañas ante nosotros, pero la misión es más "
"importante. Procedamos a esta nueva habitación."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/09_Spider_Maze.cfg:868
msgid "I think we killed all the spiders living in this part of Uvju's cross."
msgstr ""
"Creo que matamos a todas las arañas viviendo en esta parte de la cruz de "
"Uvju."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/09_Spider_Maze.cfg:876
msgid ""
"Let's take it, we will need it for our journey. \n"
"Now, let's proceed to the next room."
msgstr ""
"Tomémoslo, lo necesitaremos para nuestro viaje. \n"
"Ahora, procedamos a la siguiente habitación."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/09_Spider_Maze.cfg:912
msgid "This place is a maze!"
msgstr "¡Este lugar es un laberinto!"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/09_Spider_Maze.cfg:916
msgid ""
"We spend too much time in there. And we don't even know for sure the exit "
"still exists."
msgstr ""
"Pasamos demasiado tiempo aquí. Y ni siquiera sabemos con seguridad si la "
"salida aún existe."

#. [scenario], id=10_Great_Hall
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:4
msgid "Great Hall"
msgstr "Gran Salón"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:454
msgid "Wahoo! This room is huge! I'm pretty sure it must be nice to visit."
msgstr ""
"¡Wahoo! ¡Esta habitación es enorme! Estoy seguro de que debe ser bonito "
"visitarla."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:461
msgid "Or at least it would be if it wasn't full of spiders and undead."
msgstr "O al menos lo sería si no estuviera llena de arañas y no-muertos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:465
msgid "Let's find a way out. I'm getting really tired of all those spiders."
msgstr "Busquemos una salida. Me estoy cansando mucho de todas esas arañas."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:582
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:628
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:785
msgid "Some spiders are born from this sack."
msgstr "Algunas arañas nacen de este saco."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:766
msgid "A lot of spiders!"
msgstr "¡Muchas arañas!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:958
msgid ""
"I think I found another elevator! Let's see if this one goes back to the "
"surface."
msgstr ""
"¡Creo que encontré otro elevador! Veamos si este va de vuelta a la "
"superficie."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:962
msgid "I can see the, sun up there. Hurrah!"
msgstr "¡Puedo ver el sol allá arriba. ¡Hurra!"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:983
msgid ""
"This looks like a bigger version of the spiders. It must be their queen or "
"something like that."
msgstr ""
"Esto parece una versión más grande de las arañas. Debe ser su reina o algo "
"así."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:1005
msgid ""
"Let's go back up. We should arrive on the other side of Yooradweak's pass."
msgstr ""
"Subamos de nuevo. Deberíamos llegar al otro lado del paso de Yooradweak."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:1042
msgid ""
"I think we killed all the remaining spiders of Uvju's cross. It should be "
"easier to cross for others now."
msgstr ""
"Creo que matamos a todas las arañas restantes de la cruz de Uvju. Debería "
"ser más fácil cruzarla para otros ahora."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:1050
msgid "Let's take it, we will need it for our journey."
msgstr "Tomémoslo, lo necesitaremos para nuestro viaje."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:1100
msgid "Too many spiders. Too many undead."
msgstr "Demasiadas arañas. Demasiados no-muertos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:1104
msgid "This place is too huge. The exit could be anywhere."
msgstr ""
"Este lugar es demasiado enorme. La salida podría estar en cualquier lugar."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/10_Great_Hall.cfg:1108
msgid "We won't get out of here alive."
msgstr "No saldremos de aquí vivos."

#. [scenario], id=11_Qyizu
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:4
msgid "Qyizu"
msgstr "Qyizu"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:49
msgid "Save at least one dwarf"
msgstr "Salva al menos un enano"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:59
msgid "Talk to Amin"
msgstr "Habla con Amin"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:77
msgid "Talk to a dwarf"
msgstr "Habla con un enano"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:95
msgid "Enter the mine"
msgstr "Entra a la mina"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:110
msgid "Open the door of Yooradweak's pass"
msgstr "Abre la puerta del paso de Yooradweak"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:110
msgid "(100 gold)"
msgstr "(100 oro)"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:121
msgid "Every dwarf dies"
msgstr "Todos los enanos mueren"

#. [side], type=Dwarvish Fighter
#. [side]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:354
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/15_Ups_and_Downs.cfg:280
msgid "Dwarves"
msgstr "Enanos"

#. [side], type=Sergeant
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:429
msgid "Zei guards"
msgstr "Guardias de Zei"

#. [side], type=Peasant
#. [side], type=Trapper
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:445
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:330
msgid "Merchants"
msgstr "Mercaderes"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:472
msgid ""
"Well, it looks like the secret entrance is in a house on the other side."
msgstr "Bueno, parece que la entrada secreta está en una casa al otro lado."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:476
msgid "And outside more orcs."
msgstr "Y afuera más orcos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:480
msgid "What a surprise."
msgstr "Qué sorpresa."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:488
msgid ""
"Wait! It looks like a few dwarves are getting attacked by the orcs! We need "
"to save them!"
msgstr ""
"¡Espera! ¡Parece que unos pocos enanos están siendo atacados por los orcos! "
"¡Necesitamos salvarlos!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:529
msgid ""
"East: Zei\n"
"South: Qyizu, Udxatfe\n"
"North-west: Uvju’s Cross, western tower"
msgstr ""
"Este: Zei\n"
"Sur: Qyizu, Udxatfe\n"
"Noroeste: Cruz de Uvju, torre oeste"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:554
msgid ""
"It looks like the door is blocked by rocks. There's a barrel full of powder "
"next to them. Should I light it up?"
msgstr ""
"Parece que la puerta está bloqueada por rocas. Hay un barril lleno de polvo "
"junto a ellas. ¿Debo encenderlo?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:601
msgid "The door is now cleared. Should I open it?"
msgstr "La puerta ahora está despejada. ¿Debo abrirla?"

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:637
msgid "Well, we were trying to find a way to open this door."
msgstr "Bueno, intentábamos encontrar una forma de abrir esta puerta."

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:641
msgid ""
"You must be the reckless farmer my guards talk to me about. I wouldn’t ’ve "
"believed it if I hadn’t seen it with my own eyes."
msgstr ""
"Debes ser el granjero imprudente del que me hablan mis guardias. No lo "
"habría creído si no lo hubiera visto con mis propios ojos."

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:645
msgid "Tell me, have you really killed all these orcs?"
msgstr "Dime, ¿realmente mataste a todos estos orcos?"

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:653
msgid ""
"Zei is hugely indebted to you, pal. We will do our best to keep the lands "
"you’ve conquered for us."
msgstr ""
"Zei está enormemente en deuda contigo, amigo. Haremos lo mejor para mantener "
"las tierras que has conquistado para nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:664
msgid "Here is a little reward for having opened the door."
msgstr "Aquí tienes una pequeña recompensa por haber abierto la puerta."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:688
msgid ""
"West: Qyizu's mines, Udxatfe\n"
"                        South-east: Zei"
msgstr ""
"Oeste: Minas de Qyizu, Udxatfe\n"
"                        Sureste: Zei"

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:710
msgid ""
"Wuz crackalackin'. If you wanna git all up in Zei, itz pointless. I heard "
"tha city was burnt some nights ago."
msgstr ""
"¿Qué pasa? Si quieres entrar a Zei, es inútil. Escuché que la ciudad fue "
"quemada hace algunas noches."

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:714
msgid ""
"We is thinin bout tha way we is goin ta feed our mulez until tha arrival of "
"our associates. "
msgstr ""
"Estamos pensando en la forma de alimentar a nuestras mulas hasta la llegada "
"de nuestros asociados. "

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:718
msgid "To drop a rhyme tha real deal, one mule should be enough now, nahmeean?"
msgstr ""
"Para decir la verdad, una mula debería ser suficiente ahora, ¿entiendes?"

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:768
msgid ""
"I be S-O-Double-Rizzy, bizzy yizzy dizzy have enizzle monizzle (You do not "
"have enough gold)."
msgstr ""
"Soy S-O-Double-Rizzy, ocupado y mareado no tienes suficiente dinero (No "
"tienes suficiente oro)."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:829
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:972
msgid "It’s a rough job, but we must live. Besides, we’re not the only ones…"
msgstr "Es un trabajo duro, pero debemos vivir. Además, no somos los únicos…"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:839
msgid "I'm sorry we couldn't save more of you."
msgstr "Lo siento, no pudimos salvar a más de ustedes."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:845
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:988
msgid "What were those orcs doing here?"
msgstr "¿Qué hacían esos orcos aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:849
msgid ""
"They were looking for magical items. And where do you think the magical "
"items the orcs are stealing go? They end up in the pocket of a Commander "
"Isut."
msgstr ""
"Buscaban objetos mágicos. ¿Y dónde crees que van los objetos mágicos que los "
"orcos están robando? Terminan en el bolsillo de un Comandante Isut."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:853
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:996
msgid "May I be turn into a mule if there is no goblin in all this! "
msgstr "¡Que me convierta en una mula si no hay un goblin en todo esto! "

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:857
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1000
msgid "You seem to know a lot about what is happening."
msgstr "Parece que sabes mucho sobre lo que está pasando."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:861
msgid ""
"My brother Hufifa must know more but the orcs locked him up down there. I "
"would need your help to free him if you agree."
msgstr ""
"Mi hermano Hufifa debe saber más pero los orcos lo encerraron allá abajo. "
"Necesitaría tu ayuda para liberarlo si estás de acuerdo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:865
msgid ""
"I'm sorry, but we need to reach Udxatfe as fast as possible. We don't have "
"the time to enter the mine to look for your brother."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento, pero necesitamos llegar a Udxatfe lo más rápido posible. No "
"tenemos tiempo para entrar a la mina a buscar a tu hermano."

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:870
msgid ""
"Don't worry. The way to Udxatfe is through the lower level of the mine. "
"That's where my brother is locked. I will show you the way."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes. El camino a Udxatfe es a través del nivel inferior de la "
"mina. Allí es donde está encerrado mi hermano. Te mostraré el camino."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:982
msgid "I'm sorry when couldn't save more of you."
msgstr "Lo siento, no pudimos salvar a más de ustedes."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:992
msgid ""
"They were looking for magical items. And where do you think go the magical "
"items the orcs are stealing? They end in the pocket of a Commander Isut. "
msgstr ""
"Buscaban objetos mágicos. ¿Y dónde crees que van los objetos mágicos que los "
"orcos están robando? Terminan en el bolsillo de un Comandante Isut. "

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1004
msgid "Hufifa must know more but the orcs locked him up down there."
msgstr "Hufifa debe saber más pero los orcos lo encerraron allá abajo."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1008
msgid ""
"I'm sorry, but we need to reach Udxatfe as fast as possible. We don't have "
"the time to enter the mine to look for your friend."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento, pero necesitamos llegar a Udxatfe lo más rápido posible. No "
"tenemos tiempo para entrar a la mina a buscar a tu amigo."

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1012
msgid ""
"Don't worry. The way to Udxatfe is through the lower level of the mine. "
"That's where Hufifa is locked"
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes. El camino a Udxatfe es a través del nivel inferior de la "
"mina. Allí es donde está encerrado Hufifa"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1135
msgid "You can no longer recruit nor recall Sergeants."
msgstr "Ya no puedes reclutar ni reincorporar Sargentos."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1205
msgid ""
"The dwarves are all dead! How can we imagine saving the country if we can't "
"even save a few persons?"
msgstr ""
"¡Los enanos están todos muertos! ¿Cómo podemos imaginar salvar el país si no "
"podemos ni salvar a unas pocas personas?"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1250
msgid "My good friend! Our meeting is certainly a sign of fate."
msgstr ""
"¡Mi buen amigo! Nuestro encuentro es ciertamente una señal del destino."

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1254
msgid ""
"I need some items to bring them to my… hmmm… commercial partners… and you "
"totally look like you have some."
msgstr ""
"Necesito algunos objetos para llevarlos a mis… hmm… socios comerciales… y tú "
"pareces totalmente tener algunos."

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1262
msgid ""
"Yes, truly, you have what I need. Would you consent selling me some in "
"exchange for a substantial sum?"
msgstr ""
"Sí, verdaderamente, tienes lo que necesito. ¿Consentirías venderme algunos a "
"cambio de una suma sustancial?"

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter2/11_Qyizu.cfg:1300
msgid "I notably look for magic goods. If you have some, of course."
msgstr "Notablemente busco bienes mágicos. Si tienes algunos, por supuesto."

