msgstr "¡Aaaaaaahhhh!"

#. [1]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/21_Frozen_Chasm.cfg:217
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter4/26_Echo_Chamber.cfg:522
msgid "Oh my god! He fell in a crevasse."
msgstr "¡Dios mío! Cayó en una grieta."

#. [scenario], id=22_Ice_Prison
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/22_Ice_Prison.cfg:4
msgid "Ice_Prison"
msgstr "Prisión_de_Hielo"

#. [side]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/22_Ice_Prison.cfg:426
msgid "Teumiuxe"
msgstr "Teumiuxe"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/22_Ice_Prison.cfg:479
msgid ""
"North: Udxatfe \n"
"South: Abxoowbu’s trading post"
msgstr ""
"Norte: Udxatfe \n"
"Sur: Puesto comercial de Abxoowbu"

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/22_Ice_Prison.cfg:737
msgid "This is a good choice. Let’s end the mess I started."
msgstr "Esta es una buena elección. Terminemos el desastre que comencé."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/22_Ice_Prison.cfg:753
msgid ""
"Don’t you see what is happening? The fate of the whole kingdom is at stake."
msgstr "¿No ves qué está pasando? El destino de todo el reino está en juego."

#. [message], speaker=Teumiuxe
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/22_Ice_Prison.cfg:757
msgid ""
"If you don’t have the guts to help me save all these people, I’ll find "
"someone who do."
msgstr ""
"Si no tienes las agallas para ayudarme a salvar a toda esta gente, "
"encontraré a alguien que lo haga."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/22_Ice_Prison.cfg:777
msgid ""
"The great mage having succeeded in freeing himself from its ice grave, it is "
"clear now that a maleficent spirit manipulates the forces rampaging the "
"kingdom."
msgstr ""
"Tras haber logrado el gran mago liberarse de su tumba de hielo, ahora es "
"evidente que un espíritu maligno manipula las fuerzas que asolan el reino."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/22_Ice_Prison.cfg:781
msgid "Our heroes went looking for clues on the hide of the protection staff."
msgstr ""
"Nuestros héroes fueron en busca de pistas sobre el escondite del bastón de "
"protección."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/22_Ice_Prison.cfg:785
msgid "TO BE CONTINUED"
msgstr "CONTINUARÁ"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/22_Ice_Prison.cfg:799
msgid "Still no trace of Teumiuxe. "
msgstr "Aún no hay rastro de Teumiuxe. "

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter3/22_Ice_Prison.cfg:803
msgid "I'm afraid we have to go back to Udxatfe to announce that we failed... "
msgstr "Temo que tengamos que volver a Udxatfe para anunciar que fallamos... "

