#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:890
msgid "The Great Mage!"
msgstr "¡El Gran Mago!"

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:894
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:960
msgid "By Of’s shield, is the Guardian sending you?"
msgstr "¿Por el escudo de Of, el Guardián te envía?"

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:906
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:972
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, we are in the middle of nowhere. Our detachment left Oof "
"fortress to try to get emergency reinforcement from Udxatfe."
msgstr ""
"Desafortunadamente, estamos en medio de la nada. Nuestro destacamento dejó "
"la fortaleza de Oof para intentar obtener refuerzos de emergencia de Udxatfe."

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:910
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:976
msgid ""
"Four days ago, a necromancer with terrible powers by the name of Isut "
"appeared and fell onto us, flanked by undead and Dunefolk. The Dunefolk "
"outnumbering us, they blocked access to Idaamub’s castle from the east and "
"we got blocked from both sides."
msgstr ""
"Hace cuatro días, un nigromante con poderes terribles llamado Isut apareció "
"y cayó sobre nosotros, flanqueado por no-muertos y Barjanes. Los Barjanes "
"superándonos en número, bloquearon el acceso al castillo de Idaamub desde el "
"este y nos bloquearon de ambos lados."

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:918
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:984
msgid ""
"The six of us left by the old temple road to dodge Isut, but we fell onto "
"one of his tentacle guardians, which did not spare us. We both took refuge "
"here, but it is impossible to bring reinforcement from the legion to captain "
"Soimaql on time."
msgstr ""
"Los seis salimos por el camino del templo antiguo para esquivar a Isut, pero "
"caímos en uno de sus guardianes tentáculo, que no nos perdonó. Ambos nos "
"refugiamos aquí, pero es imposible llevar refuerzos de la legión al capitán "
"Soimaql a tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:926
msgid ""
"I know who you are, I think you should be a match for Isut. You could give "
"my comrades the boost they need to stop this monster before he kills us all."
msgstr ""
"Sé quién eres, creo que deberías ser un rival para Isut. Podrías dar a mis "
"camaradas el impulso que necesitan para detener a este monstruo antes de que "
"nos mate a todos."

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:950
msgid "Sir, yes, Sir!"
msgstr "¡Señor, sí, señor!"

#. [message], speaker=Durissa
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/scenarios/chapter5/35_Scavengers_Trading_Post.cfg:992
msgid ""
"I don’t know who you are, but if you’re as competent as you look like, I "
"think you should be a match for Isut. You could give my comrades the boost "
"they need to stop this monster before he kills us all."
msgstr ""
"No sé quién eres, pero si eres tan competente como pareces, creo que "
"deberías ser un rival para Isut. Podrías dar a mis camaradas el impulso que "
"necesitan para detener a este monstruo antes de que nos mate a todos."

