#. [unit_type], id=Ancient Dark Wose LoI, race=wose
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ancient_Dark_Wose.cfg:4
msgid "Ancient Dark Wose"
msgstr "Wose Oscuro Antiguo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ancient Dark Wose LoI, race=wose
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ancient_Dark_Wose.cfg:16
msgid ""
"It has always been all too known to all creatures that nature is not only a "
"nurturing mother; it can also be cruel, violent and destructive. It's "
"unknown what makes a wose become corrupted, but one thing is certain: "
"nowhere else does nature's rage becomes more evident than in an Ancient Dark "
"Wose."
msgstr ""
"Siempre ha sido bien conocido por todas las criaturas que la naturaleza no "
"solo es una madre nutricia; también puede ser cruel, violenta y destructiva. "
"Se desconoce qué hace que un wose se corrompa, pero una cosa es cierta: en "
"ningún otro lugar la ira de la naturaleza se hace más evidente que en un "
"Wose Oscuro Antiguo."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ancient_Dark_Wose.cfg:31
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/HerbDiseased.cfg:29
msgid "crush"
msgstr "aplastar"

#. [unit_type], id=Direrat LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Direrat.cfg:4
msgid "Direrat"
msgstr "Rata Terrible"

#. [unit_type], id=Direrat LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Direrat.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Much larger than the giant rats which often inhabit caves, these vermin can "
"injure an armed civilian, and can prove frustratingly aggressive on any "
"footing. On top of being notably very aggressive at night, these creatures "
"pose much of a threat to any serious fighter."
msgstr ""
"Mucho más grandes que las ratas gigantes que a menudo habitan en cuevas, "
"estos bichos pueden herir a un civil armado, y pueden resultar "
"frustrantemente agresivos en cualquier terreno. Además de ser notablemente "
"muy agresivos por la noche, estas criaturas representan una gran amenaza "
"para cualquier guerrero serio."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#. [attack], type=pierce, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Direrat.cfg:24 Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Fury.cfg:46
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Hellboar.cfg:50
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Wyvern.cfg:101
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/d3_Medusa_Witch.cfg:43
msgid "bite"
msgstr "mordida"

#. [unit_type], id=Gobot Dragonguard LoI, race=steelhive
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Dragonguard.cfg:4
msgid "Gobot Dragonguard"
msgstr "Guardia Dragón Gobot"

#. [unit_type], id=Gobot Dragonguard LoI, race=steelhive
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Dragonguard.cfg:18
msgid ""
"It is not clear why the Dragonguards are called what they are, a name stolen "
"from the dwarves. Some speculate that the name comes from their weapon of "
"choice, these strange staves that belch fire and death. Others have surmised "
"that it is because such weapons would be a threat against even a true "
"Dragon, should such a thing be seen again in the known world. Whatever the "
"case, it is for these weapons that the guardians of the great Goblin "
"citadels are both renowned and feared; weapons that have broken the "
"mightiest of warriors with a storm of blows."
msgstr ""
"No está claro por qué los Guardias Dragón se llaman así, un nombre robado de "
"los enanos. Algunos especulan que el nombre viene de su arma preferida, "
"estos extraños bastones que eructan fuego y muerte. Otros han supuesto que "
"es porque tales armas serían una amenaza incluso contra un verdadero Dragón, "
"si tal cosa se viera de nuevo en el mundo conocido. Sea como sea, es por "
"estas armas que los guardianes de las grandes ciudadelas goblin son tanto "
"renombrados como temidos; armas que han roto a los guerreros más poderosos "
"con una tormenta de golpes."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Dragonguard.cfg:27
msgid "thunderstick"
msgstr "bastón trueno"

#. [unit_type], id=Elder Dark Wose LoI, race=wose
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Elder_Dark_Wose.cfg:4
msgid "Elder Dark Wose"
msgstr "Wose Anciano Oscuro"

#. [unit_type], id=Elder Dark Wose LoI, race=wose
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Elder_Dark_Wose.cfg:16
msgid ""
"Filled with hatred and malice, these beings will destroy anything that is "
"foolish enough to stand in their way."
msgstr ""
"Llenos de odio y malicia, estos seres destruirán cualquier cosa lo "
"suficientemente imprudente como para interponerse en su camino."

#. [unit_type], id=Foul Dark Wose LoI, race=wose
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Foul_Dark_Wose.cfg:4
msgid "Foul Dark Wose"
msgstr "Wose Oscuro Corrupto"

#. [unit_type], id=Foul Dark Wose LoI, race=wose
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Foul_Dark_Wose.cfg:16
msgid ""
"When a Dark Wose lives long enough, its corruption makes it rot from the "
"inside. This is making it even more powerful and aggressive."
msgstr ""
"Cuando un Wose Oscuro vive el tiempo suficiente, su corrupción lo hace "
"pudrirse desde el interior. Esto lo vuelve aún más poderoso y agresivo."

#. [unit_type], id=Frozen Lich LoI, race=undead
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Frozen_Lich.cfg:4
msgid "Frozen Lich"
msgstr "Liche Congelado"

#. [unit_type], id=Frozen Lich LoI, race=undead
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Frozen_Lich.cfg:29
msgid ""
"A lich is the physical embodiment of black magic’s first goal: the quest to "
"achieve immortality. Though a great deal is sacrificed in the rebirth, in "
"becoming a lich one cheats death of that which truly gives it terror. For it "
"is the mind that is retained, and the spirit which follows, though the body "
"may wither away.\n"
"\n"
"It is not known, save perhaps by the inner circles of necromancy, whether "
"life is prolonged indefinitely or simply extended. The fact that this "
"question can be raised at all is a testament to the magnitude of what their "
"order has achieved.\n"
"\n"
"This lich transformed in the Ice Cave, conferring it specails powers based "
"on cold."
msgstr ""
"Un liche es la encarnación física del primer objetivo de la magia negra: la "
"búsqueda de la inmortalidad. Aunque se sacrifica mucho en el renacimiento, "
"al convertirse en un liche uno engaña a la muerte de aquello que "
"verdaderamente le da terror. Porque es la mente la que se retiene, y el "
"espíritu que la sigue, aunque el cuerpo pueda marchitarse.\n"
"\n"
"No se sabe, salvo quizás por los círculos internos de la nigromancia, si la "
"vida se prolonga indefinidamente o simplemente se extiende. El hecho de que "
"esta pregunta pueda plantearse es un testimonio de la magnitud de lo que su "
"orden ha logrado.\n"
"\n"
"Este liche se transformó en la Cueva de Hielo, confiriéndole poderes "
"especiales basados en el frío."

#. [attack], type=cold, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Frozen_Lich.cfg:45
msgid "cold touch"
msgstr "toque frío"

#. [attack], type=cold, range=ranged
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Frozen_Lich.cfg:57
msgid "chill tempest"
msgstr "tormenta helada"

#. [unit_type], id=Fury LoI, race=demon-loti, gender=female
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Fury.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Furies were once very beautiful beings, legend said that a man who looked at "
"them was not able to keep a clear mind because of their beauty. But when "
"they turned against the gods they were cursed and turned into monstrosities. "
"Their gaze is so terrible that any being looking at them will be paralyzed "
"in fear. They are sourrounded by a dark aura that weakens and kills enemies."
msgstr ""
"Las furias alguna vez fueron seres muy hermosos, la leyenda dice que un "
"hombre que las miraba no podía mantener la mente clara debido a su belleza. "
"Pero cuando se volvieron contra los dioses fueron maldecidas y convertidas "
"en monstruosidades. Su mirada es tan terrible que cualquier ser que las mire "
"quedará paralizado de miedo. Están rodeadas por un aura oscura que debilita "
"y mata a los enemigos."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Fury.cfg:59
msgid "sword"
msgstr "espada"

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Fury.cfg:73
msgid "gaze"
msgstr "mirada"

#. [attack], type=cold, range=ranged
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Fury.cfg:87 Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Fury.cfg:101
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/d3_Medusa_Witch.cfg:57
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/d3_Medusa_Witch.cfg:71
msgid "petrify"
msgstr "petrificar"

#. [petrifies]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Fury.cfg:110
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/d3_Medusa_Witch.cfg:80
msgid "petrifies"
msgstr "petrifica"

#. [petrifies]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Fury.cfg:111
msgid ""
"Petrify:\n"
"                        This attack petrifies the target, turning it to "
"stone. Units that have been petrified may not move or attack. It will wear "
"off after a turn."
msgstr ""
"Petrificar:\n"
"                        Este ataque petrifica al objetivo, convirtiéndolo en "
"piedra. Las unidades que han sido petrificadas no pueden moverse ni atacar. "
"Se desgastará después de un turno."

#. [unit_type], id=Green Crystal LoI, race=abstraction
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Green_Crystal.cfg:5
msgid "Green Crystal"
msgstr "Cristal Verde"

#. [unit_type], id=Green Crystal LoI, race=abstraction
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Green_Crystal.cfg:31
msgid ""
"A Green Crystal is a Shard that has emerged from a high concentration of "
"mana located in a cave.\n"
"\n"
"Crystals are bound to their mana geyser, so they cannot go out of the cave "
"they were born in. Crystals are crystalline in nature and so have unusual "
"resistances. A consequence of this is their immunity to Drain, Poison and "
"Plague."
msgstr ""
"Un Cristal Verde es un Fragmento que ha surgido de una alta concentración de "
"maná ubicada en una cueva.\n"
"\n"
"Los cristales están unidos a su géiser de maná, por lo que no pueden salir "
"de la cueva en la que nacieron. Los cristales son de naturaleza cristalina y "
"por eso tienen resistencias inusuales. Una consecuencia de esto es su "
"inmunidad al Drenaje, Veneno y Plaga."

#. [unit_type], id=Gobot Grenadeer LoI, race=steelhive
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Grenadeer.cfg:4
msgid "Gobot Grenadeer"
msgstr "Granadero Gobot"

#. [unit_type], id=Gobot Grenadeer LoI, race=steelhive
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Grenadeer.cfg:18
msgid ""
"This curious machine looks like a Dwarven Thunderguards made out of metal. "
"The Dwarven Thunderguards are famed for their curious weaponry, these "
"strange staves of wood and iron that make a thunderous noise in their anger. "
"The machinations behind this weaponry are a mystery, a secret taken to the "
"grave by the dwarves of Knalga who wield them, and are assumed to have even "
"forged them. The most that is known are reports of dwarves pouring a strange "
"black dust into the mouth of their weapons, which some say is a food to fuel "
"the beast imprisoned within. It seems that goblins tried to replicate them, "
"leading to a strange machine able to shoot explosive spheres.\n"
"\n"
"Though a single shot from these ‘boomsticks’ can take several minutes to "
"prepare, the results are seen by the goblins as being well worth the wait."
msgstr ""
"Esta curiosa máquina parece un Guardia Trueno Enano hecho de metal. Los "
"Guardias Trueno Enanos son famosos por su curiosa armería, estos extraños "
"bastones de madera y hierro que hacen un ruido ensordecedor en su ira. Las "
"maquinaciones detrás de esta armería son un misterio, un secreto llevado a "
"la tumba por los enanos de Knalga que los empuñan, y se asume que incluso "
"los forjaron. Lo más que se sabe son informes de enanos vertiendo un extraño "
"polvo negro en la boca de sus armas, que algunos dicen es comida para "
"alimentar a la bestia imprisoned dentro. Parece que los goblins intentaron "
"replicarlos, llevando a una extraña máquina capaz de disparar esferas "
"explosivas.\n"
"\n"
"Aunque un solo disparo de estos «bastones boom» puede tomar varios minutos "
"en prepararse, los resultados son vistos por los goblins como bien valiosos "
"la espera."

#. [attack], type=fire, range=ranged
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Grenadeer.cfg:29
msgid "boomstick"
msgstr "bastón boom"

#. [unit_type], id=Hell Boar LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Hellboar.cfg:4
msgid "Hell Boar"
msgstr "Jabalí Infernal"

#. [unit_type], id=Hell Boar LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Hellboar.cfg:35
msgid ""
"It is said that those boars were bread by the Ocks to be used as yoke for "
"their wagons. Since those were vanquished, they found a place of residence "
"in the Black Forest, where they compete with bears for food."
msgstr ""
"Se dice que esos jabalíes fueron criados por los Ocks para usarlos como yugo "
"para sus carretas. Desde que aquellos fueron vencidos, encontraron un lugar "
"de residencia en el Bosque Negro, donde compiten con los osos por comida."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Hellboar.cfg:59
msgid "tusk"
msgstr "colmillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Diseased Herb Spirit LoI, race=wose
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/HerbDiseased.cfg:5
msgid "Diseased Herb Spirit"
msgstr "Espíritu de Hierba Enfermo"

#. [unit_type], id=Diseased Herb Spirit LoI, race=wose
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/HerbDiseased.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Most of the herb spirits use their power to repel insect infestations but a "
"few of them welcome the insects in so that they can use them as game pieces "
"or suddenly expel them as a method of attack."
msgstr ""
"La mayoría de los espíritus de hierba usan su poder para repeler "
"infestaciones de insectos, pero unos pocos los reciben para usarlos como "
"piezas de juego o expulsarlos repentinamente como método de ataque."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=ranged
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/HerbDiseased.cfg:38
msgid "swarm"
msgstr "enjambre"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Bat LoI, race=elemental
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Bat.cfg:4
msgid "Ice Bat"
msgstr "Murciélago de Hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Bat LoI, race=elemental
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Bat.cfg:20
msgid ""
"The most vicious, predatory, and successful of the creatures born in the ice "
"cave."
msgstr ""
"La más viciosa, depredadora y exitosa de las criaturas nacidas en la cueva "
"de hielo."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Bat.cfg:37
msgid "ice fangs"
msgstr "colmillos de hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Bowman LoI, race=elemental, gender=male
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Bowman.cfg:4
msgid "Ice Bowman"
msgstr "Arquero de Hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Bowman LoI, race=elemental, gender=male
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Bowman.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Born in the cold of the ice cave, ice bowmen are fearsome enemies. The great "
"strength allows them to attack with high range and power."
msgstr ""
"Nacidos en el frío de la cueva de hielo, los arqueros de hielo son enemigos "
"temibles. Su gran fuerza les permite atacar con alto alcance y poder."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Bowman.cfg:37
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Master_Bowman.cfg:37
msgid "ice longbow"
msgstr "arco largo de hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Golem LoI, race=elemental
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Golem.cfg:5
msgid "Ice Golem"
msgstr "Gólem de Hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Golem LoI, race=elemental
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Golem.cfg:31
msgid ""
"Ice elementals, once gathering enough elemental essence, can absorb more ice "
"and grow larger and stronger. Although they are weak, they can take massive "
"amounts of damage before they are destroyed to shards."
msgstr ""
"Los elementales de hielo, una vez que reúnen suficiente esencia elemental, "
"pueden absorber más hielo y crecer más grandes y fuertes. Aunque son "
"débiles, pueden recibir cantidades masivas de daño antes de ser destruidos "
"en fragmentos."

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Guard LoI, race=elemental
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Guard.cfg:4
msgid "Ice Guard"
msgstr "Guardia de Hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Guard LoI, race=elemental
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Guard.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Ice Guards are picked from the best swordsmen in the ice cave. They function "
"as bodyguards and commanders. Their reliability and mastery of close combat "
"are their best assets, for which they are well-renowned."
msgstr ""
"Los Guardias de Hielo son elegidos de los mejores espadachines en la cueva "
"de hielo. Funcionan como guardaespaldas y comandantes. Su confiabilidad y "
"maestría en el combate cuerpo a cuerpo son sus mejores activos, por los que "
"son bien renombrados."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Guard.cfg:39
msgid "ice longsword"
msgstr "espada larga de hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Troll Hero LoI, race=troll
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Hero.cfg:4
msgid "Ice Troll Hero"
msgstr "Héroe Troll de Hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Troll Hero LoI, race=troll
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Hero.cfg:16
msgid ""
"Some ice trolls are born with an exceptional share of the strength and "
"vitality that characterizes their race. In a society where might makes "
"right, those of their ilk revere them as heroes."
msgstr ""
"Algunos trolls de hielo nacen con una porción excepcional de la fuerza y "
"vitalidad que caracteriza a su raza. En una sociedad donde la fuerza hace el "
"derecho, aquellos de su tipo los reverencian como héroes."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Hero.cfg:35
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Warrior.cfg:35
msgid "hammer"
msgstr "martillo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Master Bowman LoI, race=human, gender=male
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Master_Bowman.cfg:4
msgid "Ice Master Bowman"
msgstr "Maestro Arquero de Hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Master Bowman LoI, race=human, gender=male
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Master_Bowman.cfg:32
msgid ""
"Born in the cold of the ice cave, ice master bowmen have reached the zenith "
"of their art, inasmuch as any ice bowman is capable. Armed with a great ice "
"bow, these warriors crown battalions of ice bowmen with their presence, "
"bringing down many a foe with their well-aimed shots. Of the many races in "
"the world, only the elves surpass them in archery, and their human "
"counterparts have speculated, perhaps in envy, that this is only by dint of "
"age."
msgstr ""
"Nacidos en el frío de la cueva de hielo, los maestros arqueros de hielo han "
"alcanzado el zenit de su arte, en la medida en que cualquier arquero de "
"hielo es capaz. Armados con un gran arco de hielo, estos guerreros coronan "
"batallones de arqueros de hielo con su presencia, derribando a muchos "
"enemigos con sus disparos bien apuntados. De las muchas razas en el mundo, "
"solo los elfos los superan en arquería, y sus contrapartes humanas han "
"especulado, quizás por envidia, que esto es solo por cuestión de edad."

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Swordsman LoI, race=elemental
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Swordsman.cfg:4
msgid "Ice Swordsman"
msgstr "Espadachín de Hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Swordsman LoI, race=elemental
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Swordsman.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Born into the cold of the icecave, this unit is an experienced warrior "
"equipped with a sturdy broadsword made of ice."
msgstr ""
"Nacido en el frío de la cueva de hielo, esta unidad es un guerrero "
"experimentado equipado con una robusta espada ancha hecha de hielo."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Swordsman.cfg:38
msgid "ice sword"
msgstr "espada de hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Troll LoI, race=troll
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Troll.cfg:4
msgid "Ice Troll"
msgstr "Troll de Hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Troll LoI, race=troll
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Troll.cfg:16
msgid ""
"Ice trolls are been recently discovered. It is thought that they evolved "
"from common trolls trapped in a region of freezing cold. A fully-grown ice "
"troll towers above a man, and, even unarmed, would be a great threat in "
"combat. The large clubs typically favored in fighting act as extensions of "
"their arms, used for the same purpose of mauling their prey into submission."
msgstr ""
"Los trolls de hielo han sido descubiertos recientemente. Se piensa que "
"evolucionaron de trolls comunes atrapados en una región de frío congelante. "
"Un troll de hielo completamente crecido se eleva por encima de un hombre, y, "
"incluso desarmado, sería una gran amenaza en combate. Los grandes garrotes "
"típicamente favorecidos en la lucha actúan como extensiones de sus brazos, "
"usados para el mismo propósito de mutilar a su presa hasta la sumisión."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Troll.cfg:34
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Young_Man.cfg:243
msgid "club"
msgstr "garrote"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Troll Shaman LoI, race=troll
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Troll_Shaman.cfg:4
msgid "Ice Troll Shaman"
msgstr "Chamán Troll de Hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Troll Shaman LoI, race=troll
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Troll_Shaman.cfg:33
msgid ""
"Ice trolls are been recently discovered. It is thought that they evolved "
"from common trolls trapped in a region of freezing cold. Ice troll shamans "
"are the mystical leaders of the ice trolls. Though not as strong or tough as "
"other ice trolls, their true power lies in their cold magic, which they use "
"to blast enemies with gouts of ice or to hide in the frozen forests."
msgstr ""
"Los trolls de hielo han sido descubiertos recientemente. Se piensa que "
"evolucionaron de trolls comunes atrapados en una región de frío congelante. "
"Los chamanes troll de hielo son los líderes místicos de los trolls de hielo. "
"Aunque no tan fuertes o resistentes como otros trolls de hielo, su verdadero "
"poder radica en su magia fría, que usan para explotar a los enemigos con "
"chorros de hielo o para esconderse en los bosques congelados."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Troll_Shaman.cfg:40
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Young_Man.cfg:24
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/deshra_juggernaut.cfg:30
msgid "fist"
msgstr "puño"

#. [attack], type=cold, range=ranged
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Troll_Shaman.cfg:50
msgid "ice blast"
msgstr "explosión de hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Troll Warrior LoI, race=troll
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Warrior.cfg:4
msgid "Ice Troll Warrior"
msgstr "Guerrero Troll de Hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Troll Warrior LoI, race=troll
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Warrior.cfg:28
msgid ""
"Ice trolls are been recently discovered. It is thought that they evolved "
"from common trolls trapped in a region of freezing cold. Ice trolls "
"typically neither need nor prefer to use any proper armament in combat, as "
"large ‘sticks and stones’ serve them all too well. However, ice trolls have "
"been seen on numerous occasions clad in rough-shod armor and bearing metal "
"hammers. It is speculated that orcish allies are the source and crafters of "
"these; expeditions into several forcibly-vacated ice troll caves have shown "
"little evidence of tool use, and certainly no metalworking of any kind. "
"Given how dangerous an ice troll is with its bare hands, the thought of one "
"with proper armament is entirely unsettling."
msgstr ""
"Los trolls de hielo han sido descubiertos recientemente. Se piensa que "
"evolucionaron de trolls comunes atrapados en una región de frío congelante. "
"Los trolls de hielo típicamente ni necesitan ni prefieren usar armamento "
"apropiado en combate, ya que grandes «palos y piedras» les sirven muy bien. "
"Sin embargo, los trolls de hielo han sido vistos en numerosas ocasiones "
"vestidos con armadura tosca y portando martillos de metal. Se especula que "
"aliados orcos son la fuente y artesanos de estos; expediciones a varias "
"cuevas de trolls de hielo evacuadas a la fuerza han mostrado poca evidencia "
"de uso de herramientas, y ciertamente ningún trabajo de metal. Dado lo "
"peligroso que es un troll de hielo con sus manos desnudas, el pensamiento de "
"uno con armamento apropiado es completamente inquietante."

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Wyvern LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Wyvern.cfg:8
msgid "Ice Wyvern"
msgstr "Wyvern de Hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Wyvern LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Wyvern.cfg:49
msgid ""
"Wyverns are large reptiles that resemble dragons, but are not the "
"intelligent, magical creatures. However, the fact that they are just wild "
"beasts should not cause any traveler who encounters one to dismiss the "
"threat, for they are fast and fierce when threatened or hungry.\n"
"\n"
"Although wyverns are social creatures, usually traveling in pairs or small "
"groups, their icy counterpart seems to be of solitary nature. Their hunting "
"patterns and diet are difficult to discern, for they often work with smaller "
"animals that would appear to be potential prey. That odd behavior may be an "
"adaptation to the harsh icy environments they inhabit."
msgstr ""
"Los wyverns son grandes reptiles que se asemejan a dragones, pero no son las "
"criaturas inteligentes y mágicas. Sin embargo, el hecho de que sean solo "
"bestias salvajes no debería hacer que ningún viajero que encuentre uno "
"descarte la amenaza, ya que son rápidos y feroces cuando se les amenaza o "
"tienen hambre.\n"
"\n"
"Aunque los wyverns son criaturas sociales, usualmente viajando en parejas o "
"grupos pequeños, su contraparte helada parece ser de naturaleza solitaria. "
"Sus patrones de caza y dieta son difíciles de discernir, ya que a menudo "
"trabajan con animales más pequeños que parecerían ser presas potenciales. "
"Ese comportamiento extraño puede ser una adaptación a los entornos helados "
"ásperos que habitan."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Ice_Wyvern.cfg:92
msgid "slam"
msgstr "golpe"

#. [unit_type], id=Initiate, race=human
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mage_Initiate.cfg:5
msgid "Initiate"
msgstr "Iniciado"

#. [unit_type], id=Initiate, race=human
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mage_Initiate.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Initiates belong to the few individuals who are capable of using magic and "
"who had the luck of being discovered by a mage order. The amount of studying "
"that is still ahead of them may seem intimidating, but at the same time, the "
"mere existence of this knowledge is a testament to what humanity can "
"achieve.\n"
"\n"
"Initiates are helpless in melee combat, but possess great offensive "
"potential that will grow as they get more experienced."
msgstr ""
"Los iniciados pertenecen a los pocos individuos capaces de usar magia y que "
"tuvieron la suerte de ser descubiertos por una orden de magos. La cantidad "
"de estudio que aún les espera puede parecer intimidante, pero al mismo "
"tiempo, la mera existencia de este conocimiento es un testimonio de lo que "
"la humanidad puede lograr.\n"
"\n"
"Los iniciados son indefensos en combate cuerpo a cuerpo, pero poseen un gran "
"potencial ofensivo que crecerá a medida que ganen experiencia."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mage_Initiate.cfg:28
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Warlock.cfg:32
msgid "staff"
msgstr "bastón"

#. [attack], type=fire, range=ranged
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mage_Initiate.cfg:38
msgid "missile"
msgstr "misil"

#. [female]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mage_Initiate.cfg:77
msgid "female^Initiate"
msgstr "Iniciada"

#. [unit_type], id=Saurian Matriarch LoI, race=lizard, gender=female
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Matriarch.cfg:4
msgid "female^Saurian Matriarch"
msgstr "Matriarca Sauria"

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Matriarch.cfg:27
msgid "war talon"
msgstr "garra de guerra"

#. [attack], type=cold, range=ranged
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Matriarch.cfg:36
msgid "curse"
msgstr "maldición"

#. [unit_type], id=Mehsi LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mehsi.cfg:4
msgid "Mehsi"
msgstr "Mehsi"

#. [unit_type], id=Mehsi LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mehsi.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Mehsi incite fear and awe in miners and explorers, figuring often in "
"folklore as wrathful deities of the underground. Capable of destroying carts "
"effortlessly, and possessed of seemingly endless strength and vitality, "
"these elusive leviathans are destructive and relentless to any who try to "
"combat them. Generally living in the deep, Mehsi are imposing even to the "
"elite dwarven warriors, and are the reason they seldom inhabit tunnels close "
"to the surface."
msgstr ""
"Los Mehsi incitan miedo y asombro en mineros y exploradores, figurando a "
"menudo en el folclore como deidades iracundas del subsuelo. Capaces de "
"destruir carretas sin esfuerzo, y poseídos de una fuerza y vitalidad "
"aparentemente interminable, estos leviatanes elusivos son destructivos e "
"implacables con cualquiera que intente combatirlos. Generalmente viviendo en "
"lo profundo, los Mehsi son imponentes incluso para los guerreros enanos "
"élite, y son la razón por la que rara vez habitan túneles cerca de la "
"superficie."

#. [hides], id=dig
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mehsi.cfg:28
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mine_Worm.cfg:41
msgid "dig"
msgstr "cavar"

#. [hides], id=dig
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mehsi.cfg:29
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mine_Worm.cfg:42
msgid "female^dig"
msgstr "cavada"

#. [hides], id=dig
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mehsi.cfg:30
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mine_Worm.cfg:43
msgid ""
"This unit can hide underground, and remain undetected by its enemies.\n"
"\n"
"Enemy units cannot see this unit while it is underground, except if they "
"have units next to it. Any enemy unit that first discovers this unit "
"immediately loses all its remaining movement."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad puede esconderse bajo tierra, y permanecer indetectada por sus "
"enemigos.\n"
"\n"
"Las unidades enemigas no pueden ver esta unidad mientras esté bajo tierra, "
"excepto si tienen unidades junto a ella. Cualquier unidad enemiga que "
"descubra primero esta unidad pierde inmediatamente todo su movimiento "
"restante."

#. [hides], id=dig
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mehsi.cfg:33
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mine_Worm.cfg:46
msgid ""
"On soft ground, this unit’s ambush skill renders it invisible to enemies "
"unless it is immediately adjacent or has revealed itself by attacking."
msgstr ""
"En terreno blando, la habilidad de emboscada de esta unidad la hace "
"invisible para los enemigos a menos que esté inmediatamente adyacente o se "
"haya revelado atacando."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mehsi.cfg:44
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mine_Worm.cfg:57
msgid "stings"
msgstr "aguijones"

#. [unit_type], id=Mine Worm LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mine_Worm.cfg:4
msgid "Mine Worm"
msgstr "Gusano de Mina"

#. [unit_type], id=Mine Worm LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Mine_Worm.cfg:35
msgid ""
"Scholars differ as to the ancestry of the Mine Worm. Some hold that they "
"were brought to the mine by the demons. Others hold that they have always "
"been here. What is certain is that it is wise to avoid mines where they are "
"known to congregate."
msgstr ""
"Los eruditos difieren en cuanto a la ascendencia del Gusano de Mina. Algunos "
"sostienen que fueron traídos a la mina por los demonios. Otros sostienen que "
"siempre han estado aquí. Lo que es cierto es que es sabio evitar minas donde "
"se sabe que se congregan."

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Hole LoI, race=elemental
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Pseudo_units.cfg:4
msgid "Ice Hole"
msgstr "Agujero de Hielo"

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Monolith Sword, race=elemental
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Pseudo_units.cfg:82
msgid "Ice Monolith Sword"
msgstr "Monolito de Hielo Espada"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Pseudo_units.cfg:128
msgid "What the hell! That block of ice just turned into a swordsman."
msgstr ""
"¡Qué demonios! Ese bloque de hielo acaba de convertirse en un espadachín."

#. [unit_type], id=Ice Monolith Bow, race=elemental
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Pseudo_units.cfg:161
msgid "Ice Monolith Bow"
msgstr "Monolito de Hielo Arco"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Pseudo_units.cfg:207
msgid "Great... Now there are ice blocks turning into archers too."
msgstr ""
"Genial... Ahora hay bloques de hielo convirtiéndose en arqueros también."

#. [unit_type], id=Purple Crystal LoI, race=abstraction
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Purple_Crystal.cfg:5
msgid "Purple Crystal"
msgstr "Cristal Púrpura"

#. [unit_type], id=Purple Crystal LoI, race=abstraction
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Purple_Crystal.cfg:31
msgid ""
"When too much mana concentrate in one place, a Purple Crystal natural "
"emerge. It is a sudden event, very different from the slow accumulation of "
"mana whose result is Green Crystals. \n"
"\n"
"Crystals are bound to their mana geyser, so they cannot go out of the cave "
"they were born in. Crystals are crystalline in nature and so have unusual "
"resistances. A consequence of this is their immunity to Drain, Poison and "
"Plague."
msgstr ""
"Cuando demasiado maná se concentra en un lugar, un Cristal Púrpura emerge "
"naturalmente. Es un evento repentino, muy diferente de la lenta acumulación "
"de maná cuyo resultado son Cristales Verdes. \n"
"\n"
"Los cristales están unidos a su géiser de maná, por lo que no pueden salir "
"de la cueva en la que nacieron. Los cristales son de naturaleza cristalina y "
"por eso tienen resistencias inusuales. Una consecuencia de esto es su "
"inmunidad al Drenaje, Veneno y Plaga."

#. [unit_type], id=Gobot Scorcher LoI, race=steelhive
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Scorcher.cfg:9
msgid "Gobot Scorcher"
msgstr "Gobot Incinerador"

#. [unit_type], id=Gobot Scorcher LoI, race=steelhive
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Scorcher.cfg:22
msgid ""
"This curious machine looks like a Dunefolk Scorcher made out of metal. The "
"scorcher’s moniker is derived not from the destruction they wreak on "
"adversarial formations, but on their own singed appearances. By "
"experimenting endlessly with the equipment, goblins inevitably overstep "
"their bounds at some point and scrochers are seared by the highly volatile "
"Sanbaar sap that soaks their weapons. These machines relish igniting great "
"swaths of flame on the battlefield, though this sometimes also results in "
"unintended friendly fire."
msgstr ""
"Esta curiosa máquina parece un Incinerador barján hecho de metal. El apodo "
"de los incineradores no proviene de la destrucción que causan en las "
"formaciones enemigas, sino de su propia apariencia chamuscada. Al "
"experimentar sin descanso con el equipo, los goblins inevitablemente "
"terminan excediendo los límites, y los incineradores quedan abrasados por la "
"altamente volátil savia de Sanbaar que impregna sus armas. Estas máquinas "
"disfrutan prender grandes franjas de fuego en el campo de batalla, aunque a "
"veces esto también provoca fuego amigo no intencional."

#. [unit_type], id=Scorpion Soldier LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Scorpion_Soldier.cfg:4
msgid "Scorpion Soldier"
msgstr "Soldado Escorpión"

#. [unit_type], id=Scorpion Soldier LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Scorpion_Soldier.cfg:19
msgid ""
"A giant scorpion is highly dangerous. The deadliness of this one is beyond "
"imagination."
msgstr ""
"Un escorpión gigante es altamente peligroso. La letalidad de este está más "
"allá de la imaginación."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Scorpion_Soldier.cfg:24
msgid "sting"
msgstr "aguijón"

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Scorpion_Soldier.cfg:36
msgid "pincers"
msgstr "pinzas"

#. [unit_type], id=Spiderling LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Spiderling.cfg:4
msgid "Spiderling"
msgstr "Arañita"

#. [unit_type], id=Spiderling LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Spiderling.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Right after their birth, Giant Spiders, then called Spiderling, already have "
"a decent span, comparable in size to a Giant Scorpion. Although far less "
"dangerous than their adult form, they can already be a threat to surprised "
"adventurers due to their poisonous bite and their thick, sticky web."
msgstr ""
"Justo después de su nacimiento, las Arañas Gigantes, entonces llamadas "
"Arañitas, ya tienen un tamaño decente, comparable al de un Escorpión "
"Gigante. Aunque mucho menos peligrosas que su forma adulta, ya pueden ser "
"una amenaza para aventureros sorprendidos debido a su mordida venenosa y su "
"tela gruesa y pegajosa."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Spiderling.cfg:27
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Young_Spider.cfg:27
msgid "fangs"
msgstr "colmillos"

#. [attack], type=impact, range=ranged
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Spiderling.cfg:39
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Young_Spider.cfg:39
msgid "web"
msgstr "tela"

#. [unit_type], id=Tesla Coil LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Tesla_Coil.cfg:5
msgid "Tesla Coil"
msgstr "Bobina Tesla"

#. [unit_type], id=Tesla Coil LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Tesla_Coil.cfg:36
msgid ""
"High amounts of an unknown kind of energy are created in this machine, and "
"used in an unknown way somewhere else. You have pretty much no idea what "
"this thing is meant to do. The light it creates seems to harm everyone "
"nearby."
msgstr ""
"Altas cantidades de un tipo desconocido de energía se crean en esta máquina, "
"y se usan de manera desconocida en otro lugar. No tienen idea de qué se "
"supone que haga esta cosa. La luz que crea parece dañar a todos cerca."

#. [unit_type], id=Gobot Thunderguard LoI, race=steelhive
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Thunderguard.cfg:4
msgid "Gobot Thunderguard"
msgstr "Guardia Trueno Gobot"

#. [unit_type], id=Gobot Thunderguard LoI, race=steelhive
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Thunderguard.cfg:18
msgid ""
"This curious machine looks like a Dwarven Thunderguards made out of metal. "
"The Dwarven Thunderguards are famed for their curious weaponry, these "
"strange staves of wood and iron that make a thunderous noise in their anger. "
"The machinations behind this weaponry are a mystery, a secret taken to the "
"grave by the dwarves of Knalga who wield them, and are assumed to have even "
"forged them. The most that is known are reports of dwarves pouring a strange "
"black dust into the mouth of their weapons, which some say is a food to fuel "
"the beast imprisoned within. It seems that goblins tried to replicate them, "
"leading to a strange machine able to shoot lightnings.\n"
"\n"
"Though a single shot from these ‘thundersticks’ can take several minutes to "
"prepare, the results are seen by the goblins as being well worth the wait."
msgstr ""
"Esta curiosa máquina parece un Guardia Trueno Enano hecho de metal. Los "
"Guardias Trueno Enanos son famosos por su curiosa armería, estos extraños "
"bastones de madera y hierro que hacen un ruido ensordecedor en su ira. Las "
"maquinaciones detrás de esta armería son un misterio, un secreto llevado a "
"la tumba por los enanos de Knalga que los empuñan, y se asume que incluso "
"los forjaron. Lo más que se sabe son informes de enanos vertiendo un extraño "
"polvo negro en la boca de sus armas, que algunos dicen es comida para "
"alimentar a la bestia imprisoned dentro. Parece que los goblins intentaron "
"replicarlos, llevando a una extraña máquina capaz de disparar rayos.\n"
"\n"
"Aunque un solo disparo de estos «bastones trueno» puede tomar varios minutos "
"en prepararse, los resultados son vistos por los goblins como bien valiosos "
"la espera."

#. [unit_type], id=Orcish Commander LoI, race=orc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Warlock.cfg:5
msgid "Orcish Commander"
msgstr "Comandante Orco"

#. [unit_type], id=Orcish Commander LoI, race=orc
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Warlock.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Some orcish shamans prefer to abandon their order, or are just expelled from "
"it for various reasons. Such orcs live as hermits in uninhabited places such "
"as swamps or caves. during their exile, they sometimes study the local "
"flora, learning about the properties of some herbs. Occasionally, some of "
"them get bored with their hermit lifestyle, and decided to sell their "
"services to wealthy orcish warlord. Their knowliege of herbalism is heavily "
"valued amongs their employers. They usually aren't used to heal the "
"frontline, since orcish commanders prefer to use most their troops as cannon "
"fodder. They are mostly used if the warlord who employed them is injured, or "
"if the need to keep alive a certain troop is strategically critical."
msgstr ""
"Algunos chamanes orcos prefieren abandonar su orden, o simplemente son "
"expulsados de ella por varias razones. Tales orcos viven como ermitaños en "
"lugares deshabitados como pantanos o cuevas. Durante su exilio, a veces "
"estudian la flora local, aprendiendo sobre las propiedades de algunas "
"hierbas. Ocasionalmente, algunos se aburren de su estilo de vida ermitaño, y "
"deciden vender sus servicios a señores de la guerra orcos adinerados. Su "
"conocimiento de herboristería es altamente valorado entre sus empleadores. "
"Usualmente no se usan para sanar la línea frontal, ya que los comandantes "
"orcos prefieren usar la mayoría de sus tropas como carne de cañón. Se usan "
"principalmente si el señor de la guerra que los empleó está herido, o si la "
"necesidad de mantener viva una cierta tropa es estratégicamente crítica."

#. [attack], type=fire, range=ranged
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Warlock.cfg:41
msgid "nature flare"
msgstr "destello natural"

#. [unit_type], id=Young Man LoI, race=human, gender=male
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Young_Man.cfg:4
msgid "Young Man"
msgstr "Hombre Joven"

#. [unit_type], id=Young Man LoI, race=human, gender=male
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Young_Man.cfg:17
msgid ""
"This Young Man has decided to go on an adventure. He was not trained to use "
"any weapon but is smart enough to understand how to use them. He can use "
"pitchforks, clubs, daggers and bows, but only one at a time. "
msgstr ""
"Este Hombre Joven ha decidido ir a una aventura. No fue entrenado para usar "
"ninguna arma pero es lo suficientemente inteligente para entender cómo "
"usarlas. Puede usar horquillas, garrotes, dagas y arcos, pero solo uno a la "
"vez. "

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Young_Man.cfg:49
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Young_Man.cfg:133
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Young_Man.cfg:203
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Young_Man.cfg:262
msgid "bow"
msgstr "arco"

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Young_Man.cfg:91
msgid "knife"
msgstr "cuchillo"

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=melee
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Young_Man.cfg:170
msgid "spear"
msgstr "lanza"

#. [unit_type], id=Young Giant Spider LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Young_Spider.cfg:4
msgid "Young Giant Spider"
msgstr "Araña Gigante Joven"

#. [unit_type], id=Young Giant Spider LoI, race=monster
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/Young_Spider.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Although the most encounter version is its adult form, Giant Spider are not "
"born directly as such. When they are born, they are called Spiderlings and "
"have a size similar to Giant Scorpions. They then metamorphose a first time "
"to become what we call Young Giant Spiders, that are twice the size of the "
"Spiderling, then a second time to become Giant Spiders. Although its younger "
"version tend to hide from sight, it is a formidable opponent that should not "
"be taken lightly."
msgstr ""
"Aunque la versión más encontrada es su forma adulta, las Arañas Gigantes no "
"nacen directamente como tales. Cuando nacen, se llaman Arañitas y tienen un "
"tamaño similar a los Escorpiones Gigantes. Luego metamorfosean una primera "
"vez para convertirse en lo que llamamos Arañas Gigantes Jóvenes, que son el "
"doble del tamaño de la Arañita, luego una segunda vez para convertirse en "
"Arañas Gigantes. Aunque su versión más joven tiende a esconderse de la "
"vista, es un oponente formidable que no debe tomarse a la ligera."

#. [unit_type], id=Fury Scourge LoI, race=demon-loti, gender=female
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/d3_Medusa_Witch.cfg:4
msgid "Fury Scourge"
msgstr "Furia Azote"

#. [unit_type], id=Fury Scourge LoI, race=demon-loti, gender=female
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/d3_Medusa_Witch.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Fury Scourge are juvenile Furies. Although not as deadly as their adult "
"form, they can still petrify those who dare look at them."
msgstr ""
"Las Furias Azote son furias juveniles. Aunque no son tan mortales como su "
"forma adulta, aún pueden petrificar a quienes se atreven a mirarlas."

#. [petrifies]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/d3_Medusa_Witch.cfg:81
msgid ""
"Petrify:\n"
"                                This attack petrifies the target, turning it "
"to stone. Units that have been petrified may not move or attack. The effect "
"will wear off after a turn."
msgstr ""
"Petrificar:\n"
"                                Este ataque petrifica al objetivo, "
"convirtiéndolo en piedra. Las unidades petrificadas no pueden moverse ni "
"atacar. El efecto desaparece después de un turno."

#. [unit_type], id=Deshra Juggernaut LoI, race=deshra
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/units/deshra_juggernaut.cfg:5
msgid "Deshra Juggernaut"
