#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:4245
msgid "Biography of Buxo Iova"
msgstr "Biografía de Buxo Iova"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:4250
msgid ""
"Buxo Iova has the distinction to have been declared dead more often than any "
"other soldier in the history of the 10th Legion. At Yooradweak’s pass, it "
"was said that goblin attackers had defeated him whereas he was beating them "
"to flight three days later. He was then declared dead in a snowstorm while "
"he was gone looking for Caprine, his beloved mule, to finally return, a week "
"later, starving and bothered by a hole in his shoe. \n"
"\n"
"        For his allies, stories about his death are entertainment. For his "
"enemies, the object of their desire.  In his opinion, death will only bring "
"him when he will be bored or tired of life and the Reaper better bring "
"reinforcement! \n"
"\n"
"        Brought up by a former cook of the 10th Legion, Buxo left to the "
"west of Idaamub as guide for the ofite synod at age 16. He later arrived at "
"Idaamub’s castle and shown a cover letter ordering he was given the position "
"of his mother, but he was found to be worse cook than soldier and he soon "
"found himself at the head of his section, later his company. \n"
"\n"
"        Affected to law enforcement at Oa’s gallery during the goblin "
"pretender events, Boxa found himself face to face with goblin attackers that "
"were besieging the Iron Tower of Udxatfe and he beat them alone to flight, "
"sending with only some exceptions all his men to help defend the mines. Few "
"days later, he vanquished two full sections that were trying to pass Udxatfe "
"to reach the Eastern Kingdom and successfully contained the goblin threat to "
"the bay until these lasts finally retreat.\n"
"\n"
"        Officially announcing his resignation from the army, he became the "
"guardian of the Western Kingdom, ruling the fortifications and the security "
"of Udxatfe and becoming the owner of the kingdom’s mines. Now retired, he is "
"one of the most respected strategists of the legion and is frequently "
"consulted officious ruler of south of Udxatfe."
msgstr ""
"Buxo Iova tiene la distinción de haber sido declarado muerto más veces que "
"cualquier otro soldado en la historia de la 10ª Legión. En el paso de "
"Yooradweak, se dijo que atacantes goblin lo habían derrotado mientras él los "
"ponía en fuga tres días después. Luego fue declarado muerto en una tormenta "
"de nieve mientras se había ido a buscar a Caprine, su amada mula, para "
"finalmente regresar, una semana después, hambriento y molesto por un agujero "
"en su zapato. \n"
"\n"
"        Para sus aliados, las historias sobre su muerte son entretenimiento. "
"Para sus enemigos, el objeto de su deseo. En su opinión, la muerte solo lo "
"llevará cuando esté aburrido o cansado de la vida ¡y la Parca mejor que "
"traiga refuerzos! \n"
"\n"
"        Criado por una antigua cocinera de la 10ª Legión, Buxo partió al "
"oeste de Idaamub como guía para el sínodo ofita a los 16 años. Más tarde "
"llegó al castillo de Idaamub y mostró una carta de presentación ordenando "
"que se le diera el puesto de su madre, pero se encontró que era peor "
"cocinero que soldado y pronto se encontró a la cabeza de su sección, más "
"tarde su compañía. \n"
"\n"
"        Asignado al cumplimiento de la ley en la galería de Oa durante los "
"eventos del pretendiente goblin, Boxa se encontró cara a cara con atacantes "
"goblin que estaban asediando la Torre de Hierro de Udxatfe y los puso en "
"fuga solo, enviando con solo algunas excepciones a todos sus hombres a "
"ayudar a defender las minas. Pocos días después, venció a dos secciones "
"completas que intentaban pasar Udxatfe para alcanzar el Reino Oriental y "
"contuvo exitosamente la amenaza goblin en la bahía hasta que estos últimos "
"finalmente se retiraron.\n"
"\n"
"        Anunciando oficialmente su renuncia del ejército, se convirtió en el "
"guardián del Reino Occidental, gobernando las fortificaciones y la seguridad "
"de Udxatfe y convirtiéndose en el dueño de las minas del reino. Ahora "
"retirado, es uno de los estrategas más respetados de la legión y es "
"frecuentemente consultado como gobernante oficioso del sur de Udxatfe."

