#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6260
msgid ""
"We live in a nightmare of falsehoods, and there are few who are sufficiently "
"aware to see things as they are."
msgstr ""
"Vivimos en una pesadilla de falsedades, y hay pocos que sean suficientemente "
"conscientes para ver las cosas como son."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6273
msgid "This is an aggression against me!"
msgstr "¡Esto es una agresión contra mí!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6284
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9797
msgid "An armor of righteous cause."
msgstr "Una armadura de causa justa."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6295
msgid "I will be as rough as truth."
msgstr "Seré tan áspero como la verdad."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6307
msgid "Vivacity is demanding, without understanding."
msgstr "La vivacidad es exigente, sin comprensión."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6319
msgid ""
"To have the boldness to dictate others who they shall have in their house."
msgstr "Tener la audacia de dictar a otros quiénes tendrán en su casa."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6331
msgid "They rely primarily on the valence bond."
msgstr "Se basan principalmente en el enlace de valencia."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6345
msgid "Even in the most severe places there is still wonder and beauty."
msgstr "Incluso en los lugares más severos aún hay maravilla y belleza."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6348
msgid "Rough tusked helm"
msgstr "Casco áspero con colmillos"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6356
msgid "Always say rough things."
msgstr "Siempre digan cosas ásperas."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6368
msgid "You will be Ripper, my boy."
msgstr "Serás Rasgador, mi chico."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6379
msgid "Don't waste earth."
msgstr "No desperdicien tierra."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6394
msgid "I will be rough and stern."
msgstr "Seré áspero y severo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6405
msgid "Sense is our morion."
msgstr "El sentido es nuestro morrión."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6419
msgid "<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 2 HP.</span>"
msgstr "<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 2 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6420
msgid "The fox knows many things."
msgstr "El zorro sabe muchas cosas."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6448
msgid "Boldness has made kings."
msgstr "La audacia ha hecho reyes."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6462
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 34%\n"
"        Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance to get hit decreased by 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 10 XP.</span>"
