#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6735
msgid "What did you do to make sure you kept it unscratched?"
msgstr "¿Qué hicieron para asegurarse de mantenerlo sin rasguños?"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6747
msgid "I will be rough and stern against the aggressor."
msgstr "Seré áspero y severo contra el agresor."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6760
msgid "This boldness of ours is not new."
msgstr "Esta audacia nuestra no es nueva."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6776
msgid ""
"We can turn to vivacity and fill the whole horizon of our souls with it, "
"turn with added zest to all the serious tasks which it imposes and to the "
"pure delights which here and there it affords."
msgstr ""
"Podemos volver a la vivacidad y llenar todo el horizonte de nuestras almas "
"con ella, volver con entusiasmo añadido a todas las tareas serias que impone "
"y a los puros deleites que aquí y allá ofrece."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6779
msgid "War heal"
msgstr "Sanación de guerra"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6792
msgid "Go back to fight now."
msgstr "Vuelvan a pelear ahora."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6795
msgid "Rough bliaut"
msgstr "Bliaut áspero"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6807
msgid "This bliaut is the first rough draft of history."
msgstr "Este bliaut es el primer borrador áspero de la historia."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6820
msgid "Give them any slippery stuff to tie things up with."
msgstr "Denles cualquier cosa resbaladiza para atar las cosas."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6823
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6825
msgid "200 gold"
msgstr "200 de oro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6831
msgid ""
"In war, civilians have suffered enormously as abusive armed groups have "
"enriched themselves by exploiting gold and diamonds."
msgstr ""
"En la guerra, los civiles han sufrido enormemente mientras grupos armados "
"abusivos se han enriquecido explotando oro y diamantes."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6834
msgid "Rough leather boots"
msgstr "Botas de cuero áspero"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6842
msgid "Somewhat rough."
msgstr "Algo áspero."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6845
msgid "Infallible brillant curved bow"
msgstr "Arco curvo brillante infalible"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6863
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11088
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 37 %\n"
"Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 9 XP.</span>"
