"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 37 %\n"
"Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 1%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 9 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6869
msgid "This bow has to be thought of as infallible."
msgstr "Este arco debe pensarse como infalible."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6872
msgid "Ripper claymore of increase"
msgstr "Claymore rasgadora de aumento"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6883
msgid "Lovingly ripping off."
msgstr "Rasgando con amor."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6886
msgid "Ripper linen cloth"
msgstr "Tela de lino rasgadora"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6899
msgid "Holy toledo, he ripped on him!"
msgstr "¡Santo cielo, lo rasgó!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6913
msgid "<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 4 HP.</span>"
msgstr "<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 4 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6914
msgid ""
"Let's be perfectly clear, shall we. The fox is not a little orange puppy dog "
"with doe eyes and a waggly tail. It's a disease-ridden wolf with the morals "
"of a psychopath and the teeth of a great white shark."
msgstr ""
"Seamos perfectamente claros, ¿de acuerdo? El zorro no es un perrito naranja "
"con ojos de cierva y cola meneante. Es un lobo infestado de enfermedades con "
"la moral de un psicópata y los dientes de un gran tiburón blanco."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6927
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11205
msgid "You should be put on notice that ripping you off will be tolerated."
msgstr "Deben saber que rasgarlos será tolerado."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6930
msgid "Short bow of design"
msgstr "Arco corto de diseño"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6940
