msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 21 %\n"
"Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 4 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6971
msgid "RIP its SKIN."
msgstr "RASGA su PIEL."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6974
msgid "Scale gloves"
msgstr "Guantes de escamas"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6982
msgid "You can even use them to rip flesh out of your enemy's face."
msgstr "Incluso pueden usarlos para rasgar carne de la cara de su enemigo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6985
msgid "Short reinforced bow"
msgstr "Arco corto reforzado"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:6994
msgid "With it, you can shoot as far as with a longbow."
msgstr "Con él, pueden disparar tan lejos como con un arco largo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7005
msgid "The best metal, the best leather."
msgstr "El mejor metal, el mejor cuero."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7008
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7010
msgid "300 gold"
msgstr "300 de oro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7016
msgid ""
"Most gold comes from large, industrial mines, though 15 to 20 percent of the "
"world’s gold comes from small-scale or artisanal mines."
msgstr ""
"La mayoría del oro viene de minas grandes e industriales, aunque del 15 al "
"20 por ciento del oro del mundo viene de minas a pequeña escala o "
"artesanales."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7019
msgid "Bow of increase"
msgstr "Arco de aumento"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7029
msgid ""
"Every increase of needs tends to increase one’s dependence on outside forces "
"over which one cannot have control."
msgstr ""
"Cada aumento de necesidades tiende a aumentar la dependencia de fuerzas "
"externas sobre las que no se puede tener control."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7032
msgid "Ice sword"
msgstr "Espada de hielo"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7041
msgid "A sharp piece of ice."
msgstr "Un pedazo afilado de hielo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7044
msgid "Ice bow"
msgstr "Arco de hielo"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7053
msgid "A bow made of magic ice, shooting icicles."
msgstr "Un arco hecho de hielo mágico, disparando carámbanos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7056
msgid "Organic brigandine boots"
msgstr "Botas de brigandina orgánicas"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7065
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7264
msgid ""
"Organic boots craftsmanship has always been, and continues to be, the branch "
"of craftsmanship that best connects structure with properties."
msgstr ""
"La artesanía de botas orgánicas siempre ha sido, y sigue siendo, la rama de "
"la artesanía que mejor conecta estructura con propiedades."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7068
msgid "Brigandine boots"
msgstr "Botas de brigandina"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7076
msgid "Metal and leather."
msgstr "Metal y cuero."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7079
msgid "Organic cloth of the fox"
msgstr "Tela orgánica del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7096
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%</span>\n"
"<span color='#FF99CC'>1 extra movement point</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Enemy resistance to arcane decreased by 10%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 6 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 1%</span>\n"
"<span color='#FF99CC'>1 punto de movimiento extra</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Resistencia enemiga a arcano disminuida en 10%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 6 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7100
msgid ""
"No organic being, however brilliant, understands the detailed chemical "
"working of the human mind or body very well. "
msgstr ""
"Ningún ser orgánico, por brillante que sea, entiende muy bien el trabajo "
"químico detallado de la mente o cuerpo humano."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7103
msgid "Page's shield of monstrosity"
msgstr "Escudo de monstruosidad del paje"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7112
msgid ""
"Monstrosity fascinates us because it appeals to the conservative person who "
"resides within all of us."
msgstr ""
"La monstruosidad nos fascina porque apela a la persona conservadora que "
"reside dentro de todos nosotros."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7115
msgid "Brigandine gloves of refuge"
msgstr "Guantes de brigandina de refugio"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7131
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP increased by 4 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 1%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. aumentados en 4 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7134
msgid "I feel happy, feel I have come home."
msgstr "Me siento feliz, siento que he llegado a casa."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7137
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10932
msgid "Ripper club"
msgstr "Garrote rasgador"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7147
